(1, 'Worcester Bosch', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'worcester-bosch', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1625818041.jpg', 'boiler_1623144480.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Worcester Bosch has built an enviable reputation as one of the premier manufacturers of combi, system, and regular boilers in the U.K.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Worcester Bosch&rsquo;s boiler range has won the Which? Best Buy award for an incredible 11 years. Worcester Bosch are innovators and the recent addition of the stylish LifeStyle boiler range is a statement about where boiler design needs to be.&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815674.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Which &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch&lt;/font&gt; boiler is right for &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;my home&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Worcester Bosch offers a wide range of combi, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, then you can read our blog covering just that so you know what you&rsquo;re looking for.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which boiler is best for you.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Does &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla sells Worcester Bosch boilers because Worcester Bosch boilers meet our high standards of energy efficiency, performance, reliability, and aftercare.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers a range of gas condensing boilers from Worcester Bosch including system, combination, and regular boilers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We carry all of the popular Worcester Bosch boiler models including the &lsquo;budget&rsquo; option of the Worcester Bosch 2000 series, the mid-range Worcester Bosch 4000 series and the premium Worcester Bosch LifeStyle range.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;comes with&lt;/font&gt; a WarmZilla &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch&lt;/font&gt; boiler?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Worcester Bosch boiler sold by WarmZilla comes with everything you need to get your boiler up and running.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our packages include Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless controls, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price Worcester Bosch quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also upgrade your wireless controls to a choice of smart thermostats and you can add radiators to your order - all your heating requirements with one easy online purchase.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch boiler&lt;/font&gt; cost?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The price of a Worcester Bosch boiler depends on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Other factors that will affect the cost of your Worcester Bosch boiler are whether you require your new boiler to be moved from where it used to be, and whether you require a horizontal flue or vertical flue. Other than that, your price is fixed - &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; and find out exactly how much your new Worcester Bosch boiler will cost, in a few minutes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Prices of a Worcester Bosch boiler start from &pound;1649 when purchased outright or from &pound;10.86 per month when buying your Worcester Bosch boiler on finance.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-03-27 17:17:20', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(3, 'Ideal', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'ideal', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1626254443.jpg', 'boiler_1626255010.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideal boilers were founded in 1905, giving them over 100 years of experience in delivering boilers to homes throughout the U.K.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideal offers budget-priced boilers at mid-range quality, with exceptional customer service. WarmZilla is proud to offer Ideal boilers as they meet the WarmZilla standards for reliability, price, and aftercare.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815498.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Which &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal&lt;/font&gt; boiler is right for &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;my home&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideal boilers offer a selection of combination, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, then you can read our blog so you know what you&rsquo;re looking for.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Ideal boiler is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Does &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal boilers&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers Ideal boilers because they are classed as a budget brand, but they offer very reliable boilers, parts are easy to get hold of as they are based in the U.K, they have fantastic aftercare and as an added bonus - Ideal boilers purchased from WarmZilla come with a huge 8-year warranty.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers a range of combi, system, and regular gas condensing boilers from Ideal in a range of kW options to suit small flats, apartments, and any size home. We don&rsquo;t sell commercial Ideal boilers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers the Ideal Logic boiler range, the most popular boiler range available from Ideal. The Ideal Logic range includes system, regular, and combi boilers.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What comes with an &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal boiler&lt;/font&gt; from &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideal boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, up to 8 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price Ideal boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also upgrade your wireless thermostat to a choice of smart thermostats and you can add radiators to your order - all your heating requirements with one easy online purchase.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does an &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Ideal boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you buy an Ideal boiler from WarmZilla, prices start from &pound;1549 when buying your new boiler outright, or, if you want to pay by finance, prices start from &pound;10.59 per month.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ideal boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Ideal Logic 24kW combi boiler is our cheapest Ideal boiler, starting at &pound;1549.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; and find out exactly how much your new Ideal boiler will cost, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-02 17:16:22', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(4, 'Vaillant', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'vaillant', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1623316072.jpg', 'boiler_1623147320.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Like Worcester Bosch, Vaillant are one of the few premium brand boilers out there. Vaillant boilers offer the highest quality, reliability, and performance; this is why brand loyalty is such a big factor for Vaillant.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Regular winners of Which? Best Buy awards and holders of the Quiet Mark accreditation for their quiet-running boilers.&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815469.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Which &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant&lt;/font&gt; boiler is right for &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;my home&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vaillant offers a selection of combination, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, then you can read our blog so you know what you&rsquo;re looking for.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Vaillant boiler is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla is proud to offer Vaillant boilers. Vaillant boilers meet our criteria of energy efficiency, performance, reliability, and aftercare.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers a range of combi, system, and regular gas condensing boilers from Vaillant in a range of kW options to suit small flats, apartments, and any size home. We don&rsquo;t sell commercial Vaillant boilers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers the Vaillant ecoTEC Pro and the ecoTEC Plus ranges in combi, system, and regular boiler types.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;What &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;comes with&lt;/font&gt; a WarmZilla &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant&lt;/font&gt; boiler?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;All Vaillant boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless controls, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price Vaillant boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also upgrade your wireless controls to a choice of smart thermostats and you can add radiators to your order - all your heating requirements with one easy online purchase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vaillant boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vaillant boilers from WarmZilla start from &pound;1899 when purchased outright or &pound;12.50 per month when buying your Vaillant boiler on finance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vaillant boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Vaillant EcoTec Pro 24kW is our cheapest boiler, starting at &pound;1899.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; and find out exactly how much your new Vaillant boiler will cost, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-02 17:16:46', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(5, 'Viessmann', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessmann boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessman boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'viessmann', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1619730624.png', 'boiler_1623149672.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessmann&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Viessmann offers a full range of high-quality products that represent German engineering at its finest. Extremely reliable boilers that offer great performance are one of the reasons why Viessmann regularly picks up the Which? Best Buy award.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Viessmann has a wide range of high energy-efficiency combi, system, and regular boilers available.&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815440.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Which &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessmann&lt;/font&gt; boiler is right for &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;my home&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you&rsquo;re a big fan of precision German engineering, then there will certainly be a Viessmann boiler suited to your home. Viessmann boilers are renowned for performance and reliability, Which? Brand reviews have them just behind Worcester Bosch and Vaillant but they are classed as a premium brand boiler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Viessmann manufactures a range of combi, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, check out our blog, it&rsquo;s important to know your boiler type before getting any boiler quotes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Viessmann (or any other boiler brand) boiler is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessmann&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla stocks the Viessmann 050w and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/new-viessmann-vitodens-100-w&quot;&gt;Viessmann 100w&lt;/a&gt; boiler ranges because Viessmann offers excellent reliability on boilers with very high levels of energy efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla currently offers combi gas condensing boilers from Viessmann in a range of kW options to suit small flats, apartments, and any size home.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;What comes with a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessmann&lt;/font&gt; boiler from &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Viessmann boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price Viessmann boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also upgrade your wireless thermostat to a choice of smart thermostats and you can add radiators to your order - all your heating requirements with one easy online purchase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How much does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Viessmann boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Viessmann boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a boiler quote now&lt;/a&gt; and find out exactly how much your new Viessmann boiler will cost, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-03 13:46:55', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(7, 'Baxi', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Baxi boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Baxi boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'baxi', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1623165462.jpg', 'boiler_1623138976.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Baxi&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Baxi has been manufacturing in the UK since 1866. Baxi is a part of BDR Thermea, one of Europe\'s largest manufacturers and distributors of domestic and commercial water and space heating systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Baxi boilers aim to deliver innovative, energy-efficient heating solutions and award-winning customer support. Baxi has been awarded the Which? Trusted Traders &lsquo;Approved Service&rsquo; for their customer support.&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815126.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Should I buy a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Baxi&lt;/font&gt; boiler?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Baxi boilers are solid mid-range boilers in a similar bracket to Ideal boilers. Both Baxi and Ideal are well thought of by the heating engineers that install them and both brands are considered quite reliable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;At WarmZilla we believe that Ideal has the edge over Baxi boilers as Ideal boilers are slightly cheaper and with WarmZilla your Ideal boiler comes with a massive 8-year guarantee. Baxi boilers come with a standard manufacturer\'s warranty of 7 years on their standard boilers models, increasing to 10 years on the premium models.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Baxi offers a range of combi, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, check out our blog, it&rsquo;s important to know your boiler type before getting any boiler quotes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Baxi (or another boiler brand) boiler is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Baxi&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla does not currently offer Baxi boilers, instead, we offer Ideal boilers which we feel occupy the same space in the boiler market but at more reasonable prices and with better aftercare.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Baxi boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Baxi boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Baxi EcoBlue Advance combi boiler will cost you around &pound;1,000 just for the boiler alone without installation and all the extras you get with a WarmZilla boiler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can get a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;quote on a new boiler&lt;/a&gt; with all the extras mentioned above, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-04 15:03:50', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(8, 'Potterton', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Potterton boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Potterton boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'potterton', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler1619730720.jpg', 'boiler_1623156021.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Potterton&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potterton boilers are a U.K based boiler company that has been operating since 1850. Potterton was acquired by Baxi heating in 1999 and Baxi is part of BDR Thermea Group, a European boiler manufacturer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potterton, like Baxi, are reliable mid-range boilers, you won&rsquo;t get the additional extras you would get with a Vaillant or Worcester Bosch boiler but you will get a solid boiler at a reasonable price.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815379.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Should I &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;buy&lt;/font&gt; a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Potterton&lt;/font&gt; boiler?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potterton boilers are solid mid-range boilers made by Baxi. Potterton, as you would expect, makes very similar boilers to Baxi, with similar engineer and customer feedback.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potterton (and Baxi) boilers are very reliable with no significant drawbacks. There are, however, very similar boilers in the same bracket, such as Ideal boilers, which do the same job at a slightly cheaper price.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla recommends Ideal boilers if you&rsquo;re looking for a reliable mid-range boiler. Our Ideal boilers come with a massive 8-year guarantee and start from just &pound;1549 for the Ideal Logic range, which is a great price for a mid-range boiler with the reputation and aftercare Ideal offer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potterton offers a range of combi, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, check out our blog, it&rsquo;s important to know your boiler type before getting any boiler quotes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Potterton (or another boiler brand) is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Potterton&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla does not currently offer Potterton boilers, instead, we offer Ideal boilers which we feel occupy the same space in the boiler market but at more reasonable prices and with better aftercare.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Potterton boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potterton boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Potterton Titanium combi boiler will cost you around &pound;800 just for the boiler alone without installation and all the extras you get with a WarmZilla boiler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; on a new boiler with all the extras mentioned above, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 04:12:00', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(9, 'Glow Worm', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Glow-worm boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Glow-worm boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'glow-worm', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1623250303.jpg', 'boiler_1623160320.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Glow-worm&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Glow-worm has been manufacturing boilers and heating systems for over 80 years. Glow-worm is a budget boiler brand, their boilers won&rsquo;t break the bank but they won&rsquo;t give you the reliability and performance of a premium boiler brand.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Glow-worm offers a range of combination, regular, and system boilers manufactured in the U.K, so you know it won&rsquo;t be too hard to get hold of replacement parts.&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815346.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Should I buy a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Glow-worm&lt;/font&gt; boiler?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Glow-worm boilers are a budget boiler brand, they offer cheap boilers with average build quality. The problem with Glow-worm is that if you&rsquo;re looking for a budget brand boiler, there are better ones out there. Additionally, by spending a little bit more, you can get a mid-range boiler like an Ideal, which will be a lot more reliable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla recommends Ideal boilers if you&rsquo;re looking for a reliable mid-range boiler. Our Ideal boilers come with a massive 8-year guarantee and start from just &pound;1549 for the Ideal Logic range, which is a great price for a mid-range boiler with the reputation and aftercare Ideal offer.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Glow-worm offers a range of combi, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, check out our blog, it&rsquo;s important to know your boiler type before getting any boiler quotes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Glow-worm (or another boiler brand) is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Glow-worm&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla does not currently offer Glow-worm boilers, instead, we offer Vokera boilers starting from &pound;1489 in the budget boiler category and Ideal boilers starting from &pound;1549 if you want to spend a little bit more for a bit of added reliability and build quality.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;WarmZilla Vokera boilers come with a 5-year warranty and our Ideal boilers come with an impressive 8-year warranty.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Glow-worm boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Glow-worm boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Glow-worm Energy combi boiler will cost you around &pound;1000 just for the boiler alone without installation and all the extras you get with a WarmZilla boiler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; on a new boiler with all the extras mentioned above, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 04:13:00', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(10, 'Vokera', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'vokera', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler_1623248768.png', 'boiler_1623164520.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vok&egrave;ra by Riello has been providing reliable, high-efficiency heating and hot water solutions for over 35 years, offering a comprehensive range of domestic gas boilers to suit all homes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vokera is very much a budget brand but they claim an impressive 99% reliability rate within the first two years of installation. Vokera boilers usually come with between 2 - 5 years warranty, after that it may be worthwhile taking out boiler cover.&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625815408.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Which &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera&lt;/font&gt; boiler is right for &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;my home&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vokera is a budget brand boiler. If you&rsquo;re looking for a cheap boiler then WarmZilla offers Vokera&rsquo;s starting from &pound;1489. Vokera boilers won&rsquo;t give you the performance or reliability of premium brand boilers but they are one of the best budget boilers available.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vokera manufactures a range of combi, system, and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, check out our blog, it&rsquo;s important to know your boiler type before getting any boiler quotes.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Vokera boiler is best for you.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home WarmZilla will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla stock Vokera boilers as a decent budget boiler option. Vokera boasts a 99% reliability rate during the first two years after installation. This is a high-reliability rate but with a 5-year warranty, you might be better off paying a little more and getting a boiler with a longer warranty.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers a range of combi, system, and regular gas condensing boilers from Vokera in a range of kW options to suit small flats, apartments, and any size house.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla offers the Vokera Excel combi, the most popular combi boiler available from Vokera.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What comes with a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera&lt;/font&gt; boiler from &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Any Vokera boiler sold by WarmZilla comes with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, 5 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price Vokera boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also upgrade your wireless thermostat to a choice of smart thermostats and you can add radiators to your order - all your heating requirements with one easy online purchase.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does a &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Vokera boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you buy a Vokera boiler from WarmZilla, prices start from &pound;1489 when buying your new boiler outright, or, if you want to pay by finance, prices start from &pound;9.80 per month.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Vokera boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Vokera Excel 25kW combi boiler is our cheapest Vokera boiler, starting at &pound;1489.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; and find out exactly how much your new Vokera boiler will cost, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 04:13:35', '2021-07-17 15:36:09'),
(11, 'Alpha', '&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;Currently displaying all &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Alpha boilers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt;. Use the filter to create your own custom &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Alpha boiler&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#636363&quot;&gt; search.&lt;/font&gt;', 'alpha', 'Combi, System & Regular boilers', 'boiler1619730826.png', 'boiler_1622811334.jpg', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Alpha&lt;/font&gt; Boilers&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Established over 50 years ago, Alpha has a long history, with core values of innovation, efficiency, and customer service at the forefront of their offering.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Alpha belongs to parent company Immergas, which operates in 30 countries worldwide. Immergas is the market leader in Italy where it originates, producing an impressive 7 million boilers per year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'boiler_1625814858.jpg', '&lt;h3&gt;Should I buy an &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Alpha&lt;/font&gt; boiler?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In short, probably not. Alpha is a budget boiler brand but it&rsquo;s one of the least reliable budget boiler brands, with a Which? Brand score of 45%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Alpha boilers are not well-reviewed by engineers or customers, and with plenty of choices available in the budget boiler range, WarmZilla wouldn&rsquo;t recommend purchasing an Alpha boiler.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you&rsquo;re looking for a budget boiler we would recommend the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/worcester-bosch-greenstar-2000-series-boiler-review&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch 2000 series&lt;/a&gt;, the scaled-down younger sibling of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/meet-the-worcester-8000-lifestyle-range&quot;&gt;Worcester Bosch 8000 series&lt;/a&gt;. Sure, it doesn&rsquo;t have all the bells and whistles of the 8000 series, but it&rsquo;s a very reliable boiler, from a top manufacturer - which means you&rsquo;ll get great aftercare.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/guide-to-all-ideal-gas-combi-boiler-models&quot;&gt; Ideal Logic range&lt;/a&gt; is also a great option if you don&rsquo;t want to spend a lot on a new boiler. It&rsquo;s reliable, efficient, and it comes with an impressive 8-year &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/guarantee-or-warranty&quot;&gt;warranty&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha offers a range of combi, system and regular boilers. If you aren&rsquo;t sure &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/boiler-types-explained&quot;&gt;what boiler type you have&lt;/a&gt;, check out our blog, it&rsquo;s important to know your boiler type before getting any boiler quotes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you know what boiler type you&rsquo;re looking for, you can use the WarmZilla boiler comparison function below. Just select up to 3 boilers you want to compare and you&rsquo;ll be able to compare key stats side by side to see which Alpha (or another boiler brand) is best for you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;WarmZilla survey&lt;/a&gt;, by answering a few simple questions about your home we will be able to recommend suitable boilers for your heating and hot water requirements. You can get a quote on a new boiler in just a few minutes without adding any personal details.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Do &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;WarmZilla&lt;/font&gt; sell &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Alpha&lt;/font&gt; boilers?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;WarmZilla does not currently offer Alpha boilers, instead, we offer Vokera boilers starting from &pound;1489 in the budget boiler category and Ideal boilers starting from &pound;1549 if you want to spend a little bit more for a bit of added reliability and build quality. For more info on a head-to-head between &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/vokera-vs-alpha-boilers&quot;&gt;Vokera and Alpha boilers&lt;/a&gt;, we have written a blog.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;WarmZilla Vokera boilers come with a 5-year warranty and our Ideal boilers come with an impressive 8-year warranty.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also pick up a Worcester Bosch 2000 series boiler from &pound;1699, which is a boiler bargain.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;How &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;much&lt;/font&gt; does an &lt;font color=&quot;#ff9c00&quot;&gt;Alpha boiler cost&lt;/font&gt;?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Alpha boiler prices vary depending on the model you choose and the kW output of the model you require. The Alpha E-Tec Plus combi boiler will cost you around &pound;1200 just for the boiler alone without installation and all the extras you get with a WarmZilla boiler.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boilers sold by WarmZilla come with Gas Safe installation, system filter, system cleanse, inhibitor, wireless thermostat, up to 12 years guarantee, any flues or extension kits you may need; plus, if your condensate or gas pipes require upgrading - that&rsquo;s included in your fixed price boiler quote too!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler&quot;&gt;get a quote now&lt;/a&gt; on a new boiler with all the extras mentioned above, in a few minutes using the WarmZilla online survey.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Compare Alpha  Boiler | WarmZilla', 'Use the WarmZilla boiler comparison tool to compare any Alpha boiler against each other or any other boiler brand to see which is best for your home.', '2021-04-30 04:13:46', '2021-07-24 08:27:52'),
