(1, 'London', 'Boiler installation in London', 'london', 'boilerlocation_1625817599.jpg', 0, 'boilerarea1623934932.jpg', '<h2 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Boiler Installations in <font color=\"#ff9c00\">London</font></h2><p>If you’re looking for a new boiler or a boiler replacement in London, then get a <a href=\"https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff9c00\">boiler quote</font></a> from WarmZilla.<br><br>It only takes 90 seconds to get an online boiler quote by answering a few simple questions about your home.</p>', 'boilerarea11625817599.jpg', '<h3 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Boiler replacement in <font color=\"#ff9c00\">London</font></h3><p>If you\'re looking to replace a combi, system, or regular boiler in London, then get an instant online fixed price quote from WarmZilla.</p><p><br></p><p>It only takes a couple of minutes to get a quote on a new boiler by answering some simple questions about your home, no jargon, and no boilerspeak.</p><p><br></p><p>WarmZilla will provide you with a quote on a new boiler in minutes without you needing to give any personal details or deal with any sharky salesmen.</p><p><br></p><h2 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">How does <font color=\"#ff9c00\">WarmZilla</font> work?</h2><p>WarmZilla makes buying a boiler simpler, faster, and cheaper. By removing salesmen from the process, we save a fortune, and we pass that saving on to our customers. Also, because we fit so many boilers every year, we get a good price on them, allowing us to offer our <a href=\"https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/best-boiler-price-guarantee\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff9c00\">best price boiler</font></a> guarantee. If you find a cheaper boiler price, we\'ll beat it by £50.</p><p><br></p><p>Answer some simple questions about your home in our online survey and we\'ll give you a selection of boilers that suit your requirements, choose the boiler that you like the look of, select your installation date and you\'re done.</p><p><br></p><p>The price you pay is fixed, so if your boiler installation turns out to be more complicated than we originally thought, you won\'t pay a penny more.</p><p><br></p><h3 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Where will my <font color=\"#ff9c00\">heating engineer</font> come from?</h3><p>Your Gas Safe engineer will come from London or the surrounding area. WarmZilla has a network of Gas Safe engineers around the U.K known as WarmInstallers.</p><p><br></p><p>By buying your boiler from WarmZilla, you are still supporting local tradespeople that are vetted and subcontracted by WarmZilla to fit your boiler.</p><p><br></p><h3 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Are WarmZilla <font color=\"#ff9c00\">reliable</font> boiler installers?</h3><p>WarmZilla customers think that the WarmZilla service is \'Excellent\', based on an average review score of 4.8 out of 5 on <a href=\"https://uk.trustpilot.com/review/warmzilla.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff9c00\">Trustpilot</font></a>.</p><p><br></p><p>Each and every WarmInstaller is thoroughly vetted by WarmZilla before fitting a boiler and with every boiler installation, they are required to complete a pre and post-installation checklist to ensure that each and every job is completed to very specific standards.</p><p><br></p><p>After a job is completed, we take multiple photographs which are sent to our engineering team in-house for review.</p><p><br></p><p>This is how WarmZilla ensures high standards of boiler installation, on every boiler replacement we fit.</p><p><br></p><h3 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">How <font color=\"#ff9c00\">quickly</font> can I get a <font color=\"#ff9c00\">boiler installed</font>?</h3><p>In most cases, WarmZilla can install your new boiler within 48 hours of ordering. If you are without hot water or heating, please get in touch with us. We may have additional cover in London that will allow us to fit your boiler the next day. </p><p><br></p><p>Most boiler installations are completed within one day. If it\'s a simple job like a combi to combi boiler swap then we may be able to get the job done in 4 to 5 hours.</p><p><br></p><p>If you are converting a regular or system boiler to a combi, then please allow for up to two days\' work. Our heating engineers will always do their best to leave you with heating and hot water overnight.</p><p><br></p><h3 helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">What <font color=\"#ff9c00\">boilers</font> can <font color=\"#ff9c00\">WarmZilla</font> install?</h3><p>WarmZilla install premium boiler brands such a ATAG, Worcester Bosch, Vaillant, and Viessmann. We also install budget boilers such as Ideal and Vokera. This gives a nice range of reliable boilers whatever your budget.</p><p><br></p><p>Any boiler sol