(87, 'Alpha E-Tec 28kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'alpha-e-tec-28kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>The Alpha E-Tec 28kW combi gas boiler is a compact and lightweight unit that can be easily wall-mounted and installed in a standard kitchen cupboard. </p><p><br></p><p>With an efficiency rating of 93% and ErP A-rating for heating and hot water, this combi boiler model is well known for its efficiency. Thanks to these ratings, depending on your current boilers efficiency rating, this combi boiler could help to lower your energy bills in the long run.&nbsp;</p><p><br>Combi boilers are often the more preferred choice of boiler in UK households, as they remove the need for any additional tanks or cylinders. This is because the water heater and the central heating are installed in the same unit. This makes combi boilers ideal for those who need hot water on demand as the water is ready instantly.<br><br>The Alpha E-Tec 28 has an output rating of 26.1kW for central heating and an output of 28.3kW for hot water. Although it is the least powerful in its range, don\'t let this put you off, as it is still powerful enough to heat a home with up to 15 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. If your home requires a higher demand for heating and hot water, Alpha has also designed the E-Tec 33kW combi boiler, which may be better suited to your home.</p>', 1, 11, 44, 0, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/alpha/E-Tec%20Installation%20and%20User%20Inst%2010-18.pdf', '1', '28', 'H: 712mm, W: 440mm, D: 256mm', '12.1', 'A', '7', '93', 26, '45', '<ul><li>Stainless steel heat exchanger<br></li><li>High-efficiency Grundfos pump<br></li><li>Hydroblock assembly<br></li><li>Single electrode<br></li><li>Easy-access drive change<br></li><li>NTC\'s on front pipes<br></li><li>Combined condensate &amp; pressure relief valve connection<br></li><li>Zinc plated expansion vessel to prevent corrosion</li></ul>', 'finish_1622641535.jpg', 0, '<p>Alpha boilers aren’t up to scratch when compared with other boiler brands on the market. Its reliability is average, as is its customer score. Heating engineers also tend to think its average on nearly every metric, other than whether the engineer is likely to recommend the brand, where Alpha comes out below average.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Alpha E-Tec 28kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Alpha E-Tec 28kW Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-02 20:45:35', '2021-07-21 13:30:11'),
