(94, 'Alpha E-Tec 15R Regular Gas Boiler', 'alpha-e-tec-15r-15kw-regular-gas-boiler', '<p>The Alpha E-Tec 15R has an efficiency rating of 92% and an ErP A-rating. Thanks to these ratings, this regular gas boiler could potentially help to reduce your energy bills and lower your carbon footprint.<br><br>The Alpha E-Tec 15R is the least powerful in its range, with a central heating output of 15.1kW, however, don’t let this put you off as it is still powerful enough to heat a smaller home with up to 10 radiators and one bathroom. However, if you feel that your home requires a higher demand for heating and hot water, Alpha has designed the E-Tec 20R with an output of 20kW and the E-Tec 25R with an output of 25kW, which could be better suited to your home.<br><br>It is important to note when purchasing a new or replacement regular gas boiler, that you will need to accommodate for an additional hot water storage cylinder and a cold-water storage tank, which is usually installed in the attic. As a result of these additional elements, regular boilers are not recommended for homes with limited space.</p>', 3, 11, 49, 0, 'https://www.alpha-innovation.co.uk/custom/upload/instructions/E-Tec%20R%20Installation%20and%20User%20Instructions%2011-18.pdf', '1', '15', 'H: 600mm, W: 390mm, D: 305mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '92', 15, '45', '<ul><li>A stainless-steel heat exchanger</li><li>A backlit display to give you maximum control over the boiler<br></li><li>Easy access dry-change NTCs<br></li><li>Optional external pump wiring&nbsp;<br></li><li>Same impressive features as the E-Tec System and Combi boilers<br></li><li>Easy-to-use controls</li></ul>', 'finish_1622801103.jpg', 0, '<p>Alpha boilers aren’t up to scratch when compared with other boiler brands on the market. Its reliability is average, as is its customer score. Heating engineers also tend to think its average on nearly every metric, other than whether the engineer is likely to recommend the brand, where Alpha comes out below aver