(95, 'Alpha E-Tec 20R Regular Gas Boiler', 'alpha-e-tec-20r-20kw-regular-gas-boiler', '<p>The Alpha E-Tec 20R 20kW is a regular condensing gas boiler that is compact and lightweight, meaning it can be installed neatly inside a standard kitchen cupboard, out of sight, out of mind.<br><br>Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 92% and an ErP A rating for heat, the E-Tec 20R is an extremely efficient boiler that could also help you to save money on your energy bills.<br></p><p><br></p><p>With an output of 20.4kW, the Alpha E-Tec 20R is powerful enough for a small to medium-sized home with 10-15 radiators. However, if you feel that your home requires a higher demand for heating and hot water, the Alpha E-Tec range includes the 25R which has an output rating of 25kW. If your home does not require this amount of power, then the E-Tec 15R with an output of 15.1kW, is also available.</p><p><br>It is important to note when purchasing a new or replacement regular gas boiler, that you will need to accommodate for an additional hot water storage cylinder and a cold water storage tank, which is usually installed in the attic. As a result of these additional elements, regular boilers are not recommended for homes with limited space.</p>', 3, 11, 49, 0, 'https://www.alpha-innovation.co.uk/custom/upload/instructions/E-Tec%20R%20Installation%20and%20User%20Instructions%2011-18.pdf', '1', '20', 'H: 600mm, W: 390mm, D: 305mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '93', 20, '45', '<ul><li>A stainless-steel heat exchanger<br></li><li>A backlit display to give you maximum control over the boiler<br></li><li>Easy access dry-change NTCs<br></li><li>Optional external pump wiring<br></li><li>Easy-to-use controls</li></ul>', 'finish_1622802987.jpg', 0, '<p>Alpha boilers aren’t up to scratch when compared with other boiler brands on the market. Its reliability is average, as is its customer score. Heating engineers also tend to think its average on nearly every metric, other than whether the engineer is likely t