(101, 'Baxi 224 Combi Gas Boiler', 'baxi-224-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>Combi boilers are ideal for properties where space is limited, this is because they combine both the water heater and the central heating into one single unit, making it compact and lightweight so it can be installed neatly into the space of a standard kitchen cupboard.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for both central heating and hot water, this combi boiler can help you save money on your energy bills.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Baxi 224 Combi boiler has an output of 21.8kW for central heating and an output of 24kW for hot water, making it a suitable combi boiler for homes with up to 10 radiators and a bathroom. In addition to the Baxi 224, this range also includes the Baxi 228, another combi boiler with a higher domestic hot water output range of 28kW which is more suitable for homes with a higher demand for both central heating and hot water. The central heating output for the Baxi 228 is the same as the 224 (21.8kW).</p>', 1, 7, 50, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/baxi/Baxi_200_and_400_Combi_Installation_and_Service_Manual.pdf', '1', '24', 'H: 700mm, W: 295mm, D: 279mm', '9.8', 'A', '3', '93', 24, '71', '<ul><li>Optional flue lengths, bends, and accessories</li><li>Optional stand-off frame&nbsp;</li><li>Simple hanging bracket for easy installation</li><li>Easy to use controls for maximum comfort</li><li>Compatibility with the uSense smart technology</li></ul>', 'finish_1623076939.jpg', 0, '<p>Baxi has a good reliability record and a good customer score according to the Which? annual survey. It’s also well thought of by expert heating engineers, who give Baxi good scores across the board.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Baxi is the fourth-best ranked boiler brand from the 13 included in the Which? survey. It isn’t quite good enough for a Best Buy, but it’s close and certainly one of the best of the rest.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Baxi 224 Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Baxi 224 Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-07 21:42:19', '2021-07-14 10:26:03'),
