(161, 'Glow Worm Energy Store 35kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'glow-worm-energy-store-35kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>The Glow-worm Energy 35kW Store combi boiler is an efficient and reliable condensing gas boiler. Unlike your standard combi boiler, this combi is larger in size and therefore, does not fit in a standard kitchen cupboard.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Energy 35kW Store combi boiler combines the benefits of a system store and combi boiler in one perfect package. The storage water vessels contained within the unit not only save space but also provide large properties with unlimited hot water.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 89.4% and an ErP A-rating for both heating and hot water, this combi boiler can help to reduce your carbon footprint but also help to lower your energy bills.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With a significantly high output of 35kW, this combi boiler is ideal for larger homes with multiple bathrooms and a higher demand for heating and hot water. This boiler is a high-performance boiler with a powerful 19.7 litres per minute flow rate. This is achieved using shift load technology and a mixing valve supplied with the appliance.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 9, 71, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/glowworm/energy-35-store.pdf', '1', '35', 'H: 892mm, W: 470mm, D: 570mm', '19.7', 'A', '7', '89', 35, '57', '<ul><li>An aluminium heat exchanger that can help to reduce your energy bills</li><li>Quiet Mark approval</li><li>Modern LCD display screen</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>Compatibility with MiGo, ClimaPro2 RF and the Climastat for extra comfort</li></ul>', 'finish_1623253765.jpg', 0, '<p>Glow-worm is an average boiler brand. It has an average reliability record and engineers tend to rate it about average too. Customers who own a Glow-worm tend to like it, and engineers report that it’s easy to get hold of parts and spares.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you’re considering this boiler brand