(167, 'Glow Worm Energy Regular 12kW Gas Boiler', 'glow-worm-energy-regular-12kw-gas-boiler', '<p>The Energy 12kW is a reliable regular gas boiler manufactured by Glow-worm in the UK. Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 89.3% and an ErP A-rating for central heating, this regular gas boiler could potentially help you to reduce your energy bills.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With an output of 12kW, this regular gas boiler is the least powerful in its range, however, it is ideal for smaller homes with a low demand for central heating and hot water. This regular boiler is powerful enough to heat a home with up to 10 radiators and a bathroom. If you feel that your home requires a higher demand for heating and hot water, Glow-worm has also designed the Energy Regular 15kW, 18kW, 25kW and 30kw which could be better suited to your home.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It is important to note that when buying a new or replacement regular boiler, that you will need to accommodate additional space in the attic for a cold water storage cistern, as well as a hot water cylinder, which is typically located in an airing cupboard. For this reason, we don’t recommend a regular gas boiler for homes with limited space. On the other hand, regular gas boilers are perfect for homes that require a high demand for hot water and central heating, as the hot water is stored ready for when needed.&nbsp;</p>', 3, 9, 75, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Glowworm/energy-regular.pdf', '1', '12', 'H: 600mm, W: 375mm, D: 280mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '89', 12, '57', '<ul><li>A modern LCD display for maximum clarity<br></li><li>Top and rear flue options for flexibility during installation<br></li><li>Compatibility with the entire glow-worm range of controls<br></li><li>A heat exchanger that is easy to maintain and helps to reduce your energy bills&nbsp;<br></li><li>Easy to use controls<br></li><li>Compact and lightweight design<br></li><li>Low-lift weight for easy installation</li></ul>', 'f