(168, 'Glow Worm Energy Regular 15kW Gas Boiler', 'glow-worm-energy-regular-15kw-gas-boiler', '<p>The Energy 15kW is a regular gas boiler manufactured by Glow-worm in the UK. Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 89.3% and an ErP A-rating for central heating, this regular gas boiler could potentially help you to reduce your energy bills.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With an output of 15kW, this regular gas boiler is one of the least powerful in its range, however, it is powerful enough to heat a home with up to 10 radiators and a bathroom. If you feel that you require a higher demand for heating and hot water, Glow-worm has also designed the Energy Regular 18kW, 25kW, and 30kw. Meanwhile, the 12kW is also available for those with lesser demand.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It is important to note that when buying a new or replacement regular boiler that you will need to accommodate space in the loft for an additional cold water storage cistern, as well as a hot water cylinder, which is typically located in an airing cupboard. For this reason, we don’t recommend a regular gas boiler for homes with limited space. On the other hand, regular gas boilers are perfect for homes that require a high demand for hot water and central heating, as the hot water is stored when needed.&nbsp;</p>', 3, 9, 75, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Glowworm/energy-regular.pdf', '1', '15', 'H: 600mm, W: 375mm, D: 280mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '89', 15, '57', '<ul><li>A modern LCD display for maximum clarity<br></li><li>Top and rear flue options for flexibility during installation<br></li><li>Compatibility with the entire glow-worm range of controls<br></li><li>A heat exchanger that is easy to maintain and helps to reduce your energy bills&nbsp;<br></li><li>Easy to use controls<br></li><li>Compact and lightweight design<br></li><li>Low-lift weight for easy installation</li></ul>', 'finish_1623315575.jpg', 0, '<p>Glow-worm is an average boiler brand. It has an average reliability r