(174, 'Glow Worm Energy System 12kW Gas Boiler', 'glow-worm-energy-system-12kw-gas-boiler', '<p>The Glow-worm Energy System 12kW gas boiler is a highly reliable, sleek and compact condensing unit, designed and made in the UK. The Energy System 12kW has been designed to be lightweight, meaning that it can be installed neatly into your kitchen cupboard, so you don’t have to worry about your boiler ruining the aesthetics of your kitchen.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>System gas boilers are ideal for homes that require a high demand for heating and hot water. This is because, with a system boiler, the water is supplied directly from the mains. This water is then heated and stored in a hot water storage tank, this hot water will then be sent to your radiators and your taps when needed. It is important to note when purchasing a new or replacement system gas boiler, that you will need the space in your home for the hot water storage tank, therefore, if you have a smaller home with limited space, it may be better to consider a combi boiler. The good news is that the Glow-worm Energy range is also available as a combi boiler, so that option is there for you.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Glow-worm Energy System 12kW has a high-efficiency rating of 89.3% and an ErP A-rating for heating, meaning that this boiler could not only potentially help you to reduce your carbon footprint, but could also help lower your energy bills.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This system gas boiler is the least powerful in its range when it comes to output, with an output of only 12kW. Although this combi boiler is better suited to smaller homes with less demand for heating and hot water, it is still powerful enough to heat a hot with up to 10 radiators and a bathroom. If your home has a higher demand for both central heating and hot water, the Energy System range also has outputs of 15kW, 18kW, 25kW and 35kW.&nbsp;</p>', 2, 9, 78, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Glowworm/energy-sy