(178, 'Glow-worm Energy System 30kW Gas Boiler', 'glow-worm-energy-system-30kw-gas-boiler', '<p>The Glow-worm System 30kW is the most powerful system boiler in the Energy range, with an output of 30kW. This output is powerful enough to heat a medium to larger-sized home with up to 20 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. Other available outputs include the 12kW, 15kW, 18kW and 25kW so smaller homes can also find a model to suit their requirements.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 89.3% and an ErP A-rating for central heating, this system boiler could help you to save some money on your energy bills. The Glow-worm Energy system boiler is also a compact and lightweight unit that can fit in a standard kitchen cupboard with ease, saving space in your home.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Glow-worm Energy system boiler is designed and manufactured in the UK, with the most important parts of the hot water and heating system, such as the pump and expansion vessel already built into it. Not only does this make installation easier, but also means you get a faster response to demand for heating and hot water, and you don\'t need to have a feed and expansion tank in the loft as you would need for a regular boiler.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>System boilers are great for those homes that have a high demand for both central heating and hot water. Mains water is heated and stored into a separate hot water storage tank. However, this does mean that you will need to have the extra space in your home for an additional tank when purchasing a new or replacement system boiler. For this reason, we don’t recommend them for smaller homes with limited space. </p><p><br></p><p>On the plus side, if the Glow-worm Energy range is what you want but you don\'t have space in your home, this range is also available as a combi boiler.&nbsp;<br></p>', 2, 9, 78, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Glowworm/energy-system.pdf', '1', '30', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 280m