(191, 'Ideal Logic Plus C35 Combi Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-plus-c35-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>The Ideal Logic Plus C35 is the most powerful condensing gas-fired combi boiler in the Logic Plus range. Having a combi boiler installed means there is no need for an additional hot or cold water tank in your home. This helps with quick and easy installation.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Ideal has designed the Logic Plus C35 to be compact, so it can fit neatly into a standard kitchen cupboard. With a high-efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A rating, the Ideal Logic Plus can not only help you to reduce your carbon footprint but can also help to reduce your energy bills.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Ideal Logic Plus range all have the same central heating output level of 24.2kW, however, the domestic hot water output level on each boiler model is different. As mentioned, the Ideal Logic Plus C35 is the most powerful model in the range with a hot water output of 35.3kW, this is perfect for those who have a bath in their home, or 2 bathrooms and up to 30 radiators.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>However, many smaller homes do not require this output for central heating and hot water, therefore, if you are looking for a new or replacement boiler that does not need to meet this level of demand, then the Ideal Logic Plus C24 or C30 may be a better option for you.</p>', 1, 3, 83, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/logic-1.pdf', '1', '35', 'H: 700mm, W: 395mm, D: 278mm', '14.5', 'A', '7', '94', 35, '69', '<ul><li>Large digital display<br></li><li>Easily reachable pressure gauge<br></li><li>An easy to read digital display screen<br></li><li>Honeywell gas valve&nbsp;<br></li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection for extra peace of mind&nbsp;<br></li><li>A hardwearing and scratch-resistant case for extra longevity<br></li><li>Low lift weight for easy installation&nbsp;<br></li><li>Built-in filling loop</li></ul>', 'finish_1623399589.jpg', 0, '<p>Ideal boilers