(192, 'Ideal Vogue GEN2 C26 Combi Gas Boiler', 'ideal-vogue-gen2-c26-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>The Ideal Vogue Gen2 combi boiler is an all-rounder, supplying your hot water and central heating on demand. With an output rating of 18kW for central heating and 26kW for hot water, the Ideal Vogue C26 is perfect for smaller homes with up to 15 radiators. With an efficiency rating of 93%, this combi boiler will also help on lowering your energy bills.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you are looking for a new or replacement boiler with a higher output rating, the Ideal Vogue Gen2 is also available in 26kW for central heating and 32kW for hot water (C32) and 30kW for central heating and 40kW for hot water (C40), which are both suitable for homes with a higher demand for central heating and hot water.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Ideal Vogue Gen2 combi boiler range has been designed to be compact so that it takes up a minimal amount of space in your home. This also means that this boiler can be fitted neatly into the space of a standard kitchen cupboard.</p>', 1, 3, 84, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/Installation-Vogue-Combi-Gen2.pdf', '1', '26', 'H: 740mm, W: 445mm, D: 330mm', '10.6', 'A', '8', '93', 26, '69', '<ul><li>Multi-function buttons<br></li><li>An easy to read pressure gauge<br></li><li>Cool door technology, with full-size door complete with damped opening<br></li><li>Up to 7:1 modulation<br></li><li>A stainless steel heat exchanger</li><li>A large LCD display screen</li><li>User-friendly controls<br></li><li>Low-lift weight&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1623399728.jpg', 0, '<p>Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s well worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer score, and the Which? expert heating engineers rank it above average too.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Ideal Vogue GEN2 C26 Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to k