(194, 'Ideal Vogue GEN2 C40 Combi Gas Boiler', 'ideal-vogue-gen2-c40-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>The Ideal Vogue Gen2 combi Gas boilers are perfect for properties with limited space as they don’t require an external water tank or cylinder. Its compact size and low lift weight helps for easy installation and access, meaning lower costs for maintenance or servicing in the future.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With an output rating of 32kW for central heating and 40kW for hot water, the Ideal Vogue Gen2 C40 is ideal for medium to larger-sized homes with up to 20 radiators or 2 to 3 bathrooms. However, many smaller homes would not require this demand for heating and hot water. </p><p><br></p><p>In this case, if your home has a lower demand for central heating, the Ideal Vogue Gen2 C26 which has a central heating output of 18kW and 26kW for hot water or the C32 which has an output of 26kW for central heating and 32kW for hot water, which may be better suited to your home.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Ideal Vogue Gen2 combi boiler range has been designed to be compact so that it takes up a minimal amount of space in your home, this also means that it can be fitted neatly into the space of a standard kitchen cupboard.</p>', 1, 3, 84, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/Installation-Vogue-Combi-Gen2.pdf', '1', '40', 'H: 740mm, W: 445mm, D: 330mm', '16.4', 'A', '8', '93', 40, '69', '<ul><li>Multi-function buttons<br></li><li>An easy to read pressure gauge<br></li><li>Cool door technology, with full-size door complete with damped opening<br></li><li>Up to 7:1 modulation<br></li><li>A stainless steel heat exchanger<br></li><li>A large LCD display screen<br></li><li>User-friendly controls<br></li><li>Low-lift weight&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1623400491.jpg', 0, '<p>Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s well worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good custo