(195, 'Ideal Vogue Max C26 Combi Gas Boiler', 'ideal-vogue-max-c26-combi-gas-boiler', '<p>The Ideal Vogue Max C26 is a reliable combi boiler with a high-efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for central heating and hot water. With these ratings, the Ideal Vogue Max is very efficient and could also help reduce your energy bills and carbon footprint.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With a central heating output of 18kW and a domestic hot water output rating of 26kW, the C26 is best suited to homes with around 15 radiators and a single bathroom.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Combi boilers are ideal for homes with a high demand for instant hot water. This is because the hot water is heated directly from the mains and delivered to your taps, baths and showers on demand when needed. Combi boilers are also great for homes with limited space as they are designed to remove the need for any additional cold or hot water tanks or cylinders. </p><p><br></p><p>The Ideal Vogue Max C32 is compact, enabling easy and quick installation. Although this combi boiler is a slightly larger model than some other Ideal boilers, this boiler may need to be on display but can still be wall-mounted.</p>', 1, 3, 85, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/Vogue-Max-Combi-Installation-Servicing-222378-1_lowres-REDEUCED.pdf', '1', '26', 'H: 740mm, W: 445mm, D: 330mm', '10.6', 'A', '10', '93', 26, '69', '<ul><li>Modern and compact design&nbsp;<br></li><li>An easy to read pressure gauge<br></li><li>Large control panel&nbsp;<br></li><li>A stainless steel heat exchanger<br></li><li>A large LCD display screen<br></li><li>User-friendly controls</li><li>Low-lift weight&nbsp;<br></li><li>Built-in frost protection</li></ul>', 'finish_1623401069.jpg', 0, '<p>Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s well worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer score, and the Which? expert heating en