(219, 'Ideal Mexico HE MEX 36 Regular Gas Boiler', 'ideal-mexico-he-mex-36-regular-gas-boiler', '<p>The Ideal Mexico HE MEX 36 is the most powerful floor-standing regular (heat-only) gas boiler. With an efficiency rating of 89% and an ErP A-rating for central heating and hot water, this boiler could potentially help you to lower your gas bills.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This model is the most powerful of the five boilers in the Mexico range, with an output of 37kW for central heating. This is powerful enough to heat a property with up to 20 radiators and multiple bathrooms. If you feel that your home does not require this much power, the Ideal Mexico HE MEX 15, 18, 24, and 30 (outputs between 15kW and 30kW) are also available for properties with lesser demand.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It is important to note that when purchasing a new or replacement regular boiler you will need to accommodate for an additional hot water cylinder as well as a cold water cistern and a feed. This is because regular boilers are fed with cold water directly from the cistern, which is installed in the attic of a home. This water is then heated in the unit and then transferred into a hot water cylinder to be used when needed. For this reason, we do not recommend regular gas boilers for homes with limited space.&nbsp;</p>', 3, 3, 92, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/Ideal-mexico.pdf', '1', '36', 'H: 850mm, W: 450mm, D: 530mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '89', 36, '69', '<ul><li>Designed for flexible siting and easy access for installers&nbsp;<br></li><li>Built-in frost protection for that extra reassurance during the colder months<br></li><li>Simple controls for maximum comfort&nbsp;<br></li><li>A fully backlit LCD display screen<br></li><li>Floor standing&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1623424436.jpg', 0, '<p>Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s well worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer score, and the Which? expert heating engineers rank it above average too.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Ideal Mexico HE MEX 36 Regular Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Promax SL Heat 12kW Regular Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-11 15:13:56', '2021-07-14 14:10:18'),
(220, 'Ideal Logic Max S15 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-max-s15-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Ideal Logic Max S15 system boiler is an industry-leading reliable gas boiler.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">When looking for a new or replacement boiler, it is important to look into the\r\nefficiency rating to ensure your boiler meets your demands. The Ideal Logic Max S15 has a rating of 93% and an ErP\r\nA-rating, meaning that not only is it a very reliable system boiler, but it can also help you\r\nreduce your energy bills and carbon footprint.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">With\r\nan output rating of 15kW for central heating, this model is great for smaller\r\nhomes with up to 10 radiators and a single bathroom. In addition to the Ideal Logic Max S15, the\r\nLogic Max range includes the S18, S24, and the S30 with energy outputs between 18kW and 30kW. Therefore, if your home\r\nrequires a higher demand for both central heating and hot water, then there is\r\nan option for everyone.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">A system boiler is a great\r\nchoice for homes with a higher demand for domestic hot water. This is because\r\nthe hot water is stored in a cylinder ready for use when needed. However, it</span>&nbsp;is important to note that when\r\npurchasing a new or replacement system boiler that you will need to consider\r\nspace for an additional hot water cylinder in your home which is typically\r\nlocated in an airing cupboard.&nbsp;<br></p>', 2, 3, 91, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/logic-max-system-inst.pdf', '1', '15', 'H: 700mm, W: 395mm, D: 278mm', 'N/A', 'A', '10', '93', 15, '69', '<ul><li>Built-in frost protection for extra reassurance during those winter months</li><li>A large digital LCD display screen for easy use</li><li>User-friendly heating controls</li><li>A low lift weight for easy installation</li><li>Scratch-resistant casing</li></ul>', 'finish_1623674123.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s\r\nwell worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer\r\nscore, and the Which? expert heating engineers rank it above average too.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', 'review_img1_1623675053.png', 'review_img2_1623674864.png', 'Ideal Logic Max S15 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Ideal Logic Max S15 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-14 12:35:23', '2021-07-14 13:40:56');
