(221, 'Ideal Logic Max S18 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-max-s18-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Ideal Logic Max S18 System boiler is known for\r\nbeing a highly reliable industry-leading system gas boiler, built in the UK.\r\nWith an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for central heating, the\r\nIdeal Logic Max S18 could potentially help you reduce your energy bills and\r\ncarbon footprint.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">With\r\nan output rating of 18kW for central heating, this model is great for smaller\r\nhomes with up to 10 radiators and a single bathroom. The Ideal Logic Max S18 is\r\nmiddle of the range when it comes to energy output, therefore, if you are\r\nlooking for a more powerful system boiler, the S24 or S30 may be better suited\r\nto you and your home. Meanwhile, if you’re home doesn’t require as much power,\r\nthe S15 is also available.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">A\r\nsystem boiler is a great choice for homes with a higher demand for domestic hot\r\nwater than can be met by a combi boiler. This is because a system boiler stores the hot water that is heated in the boiler unit in a separate cylinder, ready for use when needed.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Although\r\nthe boiler unit itself is compact and lightweight, it is important to note that when\r\npurchasing a new or replacement system boiler, you will need to consider space\r\nfor an additional hot water cylinder. This is usually installed in an airing\r\ncupboard.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 2, 3, 91, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/logic-max-system-inst.pdf', '1', '18', 'H: 700mm, W: 395mm, D: 278mm', 'N/A', 'A', '10', '93', 18, '69', '<ul><li>Built-in frost protection for extra reassurance during those winter months</li><li>A large digital LCD display screen for easy use</li><li>User-friendly heating controls</li><li>A low lift weight for easy installation</li><li>Scratch-resistant casing</li></ul>', 'finish_1623676207.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Ideal boilers have\r\nmade steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and\r\nIdeal is now a serious brand that’s well worth considering. Ideal has a good\r\nreliability record, a good customer score, and the Which? expert heating engineers\r\nrank it above average too.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Ideal Logic Max S18 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Ideal Logic Max S18 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-14 13:10:07', '2021-07-14 14:11:27'),
(222, 'Ideal Logic Max S24 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-max-s24-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Designed\r\nand manufactured in the UK, the Ideal Logic Max S24 system gas boiler is known\r\nfor being a reliable condensing unit with a variety of features and benefits.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">If\r\nyou are looking for a new reliable and cost-effective system boiler then thanks to its efficiency\r\nrating of 94% and an ErP A-rating, the Ideal Logic Max S24 could be a great contender. With these ratings, this boiler could also potentially help you reduce\r\nyour energy bills.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nIdeal Logix Max S24 has a central heating output rating of 24kW which makes it\r\nbest suited to medium-sized properties with between 10-15 radiators.&nbsp;</span>The\r\nIdeal Logic Max is available in lower outputs of 15kW and 18kW if your home does not require such a high demand\r\nfor central heating and hot water, while the S30 is the most powerful in the\r\nrange with a central heating output of 30 kW for homes with higher demand.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">A\r\nsystem boiler is a great choice for homes with a higher demand for domestic hot\r\nwater. This is because the boiler is fed with cold water directly from the mains, this water is then heated in your boiler unit and then stored in a cylinder ready for use when\r\nneeded. It is important to remember that when purchasing a new or replacement\r\nsystem boiler that you will need to consider space for an additional hot water\r\ncylinder in your home.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 2, 3, 91, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/logic-max-system-inst.pdf', '1', '24', 'H: 700mm, W: 395mm, D: 278mm', 'N/A', 'A', '10', '94', 24, '69', '<ul><li>Built-in frost protection for extra reassurance during those winter months</li><li>A large digital LCD display screen for easy use</li><li>User-friendly heating controls</li><li>A low lift weight for easy installation</li><li>Scratch-resistant casing</li></ul>', 'finish_1623676802.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s\r\nwell worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer\r\nscore, and the Which? expert heating engineers rank it above average too.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Ideal Logic Max S24 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Ideal Logic Max S24 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-14 13:20:02', '2021-07-14 14:18:50'),
(223, 'Ideal Logic Max S30 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-max-s30-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Designed\r\nand manufactured in the UK, the Ideal Logic Max S30 system gas boiler is a\r\nhighly reliable condensing unit with a whole load of features and benefits.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Thanks\r\nto the efficiency of 93% and Erp A-rating the Logic Max S30 system boiler has the potential\r\nto lower the energy bills and the carbon footprint of your home, depending on the efficiency rating of your current boiler.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\n30.3kW output rating offered by this model makes this system boiler the most\r\npowerful in the Logic Max range. The Ideal Logic Max S30 is perfect for larger\r\nhomes with up to 20 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. For homes with around 10 radiators and a bathroom, then the\r\nIdeal Logic Max S15 or S18 may be better suited to your needs, while\r\nthe S24 is more suitable for homes with 15 radiators and a bathroom.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">System\r\nboilers store hot water in a cylinder, which is then ready to be delivered to\r\nyour taps, showers, or baths, making them ideal for homes with a higher\r\ndemand for instant hot water.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 2, 3, 91, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/logic-max-system-inst.pdf', '1', '30', 'H: 700mm, W: 395mm, D: 278mm', 'N/A', 'A', '10', '93', 30, '69', '<ul><li>Built-in frost protection for extra reassurance during those winter months</li><li>A large digital LCD display screen for easy use</li><li>User-friendly heating controls</li><li>A low lift weight for easy installation</li><li>Scratch-resistant casing</li></ul>', 'finish_1623677184.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s\r\nwell worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer\r\nscore, and the Which? expert heating engineers rank it above average too.</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Ideal Logic Max S30 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Ideal Logic Max S30 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-14 13:26:24', '2021-07-14 14:20:37'),
(224, 'Ideal Logic Plus S15 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-plus-s15-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Ideal Logic Plus system gas boiler is referred to\r\nas the ‘flagship’ range of Ideal boilers. The\r\nIdeal Logic Plus S15 is a condensing system gas boiler that operates at a high-efficiency\r\nlevel of 93%, which is why this system boiler has been awarded an ErP A-rating\r\nfor central heating and has been endorsed by the Energy Saving Trust. With\r\nthese ratings, this boiler could potentially help you to reduce your energy\r\nbills.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">With an output rating of 15kW, the Ideal Logic Plus S15\r\nis the least powerful system boiler in its range, however, don’t let this put\r\nyou off, as this boiler is perfect for smaller homes with up to 10 radiators.\r\nHowever, if your home requires a higher demand for central heating, Ideal have\r\ndesigned the Logic Plus S18, S24, and the S30 for homes that need a larger energy output.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">A\r\nsystem boiler is the best option for homes with higher demands for domestic hot\r\nwater. This is because they store the water that is heated in a hot water tank\r\nso that it\'s ready whenever it\'s needed so that you have water ‘on tap’ (excuse\r\nthe pun). </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">However, it is important to note that when purchasing a new or replacement system boiler, you will need to have the room in your home for an additional hot water storage cylinder. These are usually installed in an airing cupboard or similar size space in your home. For this reason, system boilers are not ideal for homes with limited space.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 2, 3, 93, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/logic-plus30s.pdf', '1', '15', 'H: 700mm, W: 398mm, D: 278mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '93', 15, '69', '<ul><li>Built-in frost protection for extra reassurance during those winter months</li><li>A large digital LCD display screen for easy use</li><li>User-friendly heating controls</li><li>A low lift weight for easy installation</li><li>Scratch-resistant casing</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>LPG conversion kit is available for off-grid properties</li></ul>', 'finish_1623680042.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s\r\nwell worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer\r\nscore, and t