(225, 'Ideal Logic Plus S18 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-plus-s18-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Ideal Logic Plus is referred to as the ‘flagship’\r\nrange of Ideal boilers. <span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nLogic Plus S18 system boiler is a condensing boiler that operates at a high-efficiency level of 93% and has been awarded an ErP A-rating for heat. This system boiler is so reliable, it has been endorsed by the Energy Saving Trust.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">With an output rating of 18kW, the Ideal Logic Plus S18\r\nis mid-range regarding power. But don’t let this put you off as this system boiler still packs a punch! The Ideal Logic Plus S18 system boiler is perfect for smaller homes with up to 10 to 15 radiators and a single bathroom. If your\r\nhome requires a higher demand for central heating, Ideal have designed the\r\nLogic Plus S24 and the S30 for homes that need a larger energy output.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; ba