(231, 'Ideal Logic S24 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-logic-s24-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The Ideal Logic S24 system gas boiler has an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating, resulting in this a being highly reliable system boiler that could help you reduce your energy bills and\r\ncarbon footprint.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nIdeal Logic S24 is best suited to medium-sized homes with up to 15\r\nradiators and a bathroom. If your home has a higher demand for central heating,\r\nIdeal has designed the Logic S30, with an output of 30kW, which is perfect for\r\nhomes with up to 20 radiators. However, if you are looking for a new system\r\nboiler with a lesser output rating, the S15 (15kW) and the S18 (18kW) are\r\navailable.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nbenefit of having a system boiler is that the water is heated and stored in a\r\nhot water cylinder where it remains until you turn on a tap, bath, or shower. By\r\nworking in this way, system boilers can meet higher demands for domestic hot\r\nwater than a combi boiler - great for homes with multiple bathrooms.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 2, 3, 94, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/ideal/Logic-System-Installation-Manual.pdf', '1', '24', 'H: 700mm, W: 395mm, D: 278mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '93', 24, '69', '<ul><li>Built-in frost protection for extra reassurance during those winter months</li><li>A large digital LCD display screen for easy use</li><li>User-friendly heating controls</li><li>A low lift weight for easy installation</li><li>Scratch-resistant casing</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>10 years warranty on heat exchanger</li></ul>', 'finish_1623683510.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Ideal boilers have made steady improvements in the Which? annual survey over the past few years, and Ideal is now a serious brand that’s\r\nwell worth considering. Ideal has a good reliability record, a good customer\r\nscore, and the Which? expert heating engineers rank it above average too.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Ideal Logic S24 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Ideal Logic S24 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-14 15:11:50', '2021-07-14 13:33:09');
