(276, 'Potterton Ultra Regular 12kW Gas Boiler', 'potterton-ultra-regular-12kw-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The Potterton Ultra\r\nHeat 12kW regular gas boiler is a highly efficient unit, that has been designed\r\nto be compact and lightweight so that it can be easily wall-mounted into the\r\nspace of a standard kitchen, so you don’t have to worry about your boiler\r\nruining your aesthetics. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Thanks to\r\nits high-efficiency rating of 89.2% and an ErP A-rating for central heating,\r\nthis regular gas boiler could potentially help you to reduce your energy bills.\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">It is\r\nimportant to remember when purchasing a new or replacement regular gas boiler,\r\nthat you will need to accommodate for an additional hot water storage tank (which is typically