(282, 'Potterton Assure 12kW System Gas Boiler', 'potterton-assure-12kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure 12kW system gas boiler is a highly\r\nreliable boiler that can be wall-mounted in your standard kitchen cupboard,\r\nsaving you space in your home. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for\r\ncentral heating, the Assure 12kW can not only help you to reduce your carbon\r\nfootprint but can also help to lower your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is important to note when purchasing a new or replacement\r\nsystem boiler, that although the boiler unit itself is compact, you will need\r\nto have space for an additional sealed hot water storage tank. This is because\r\nsystem boilers are fed with cold water directly from the mains, this water is\r\nthen heated in the boiler and then it’s transferred into a sealed hot water\r\ntank for when needed. </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">However, if space in your home is not limited and you require\r\ninstant hot water, system boilers could be the perfect option for you. The\r\nPotterton Assure range is also available as a combi boiler for those with\r\nlimited space in their home. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Assure 12kW is suitable for smaller homes with up to 10\r\nradiators and a bathroom. If your home requires a higher demand, the Assure\r\n15kW, 18kW, or 24kW are available.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 8, 107, NULL, 'https://www.potterton.co.uk/-/media/websites/pottertonuk/files/potterton-assure-range-guide-january-2019-web.pdf?la=en&hash=04DFEDA59759AE13276E1D2B16854ABAC6590EF1', '1', '12', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 285mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '93', 12, '70', '<ul><li>A central flue, making installation easier and faster</li><li>Optional outdoor weather sensor</li><li>Built-in drip tray to protect against water ingress</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-life weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li></ul>', 'finish_1623842708.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Assure 12kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Assure 12kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 11:25:08', '2021-07-21 12:01:08'),
(283, 'Potterton Assure 15kW System Gas Boiler', 'potterton-assure-15kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure 15kW system gas boiler is a highly\r\nreliable boiler, with an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for\r\ncentral heating, which can not only help you to reduce your carbon footprint\r\nbut can also help to lower your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">This system boiler has been designed to be compact and\r\nlightweight so that it can be wall-mounted in your standard kitchen cupboard,\r\nsaving you space in your home. However, it is important to note when purchasing\r\na new or replacement system boiler, that although the boiler unit itself is\r\ncompact, you will need to have space for an additional sealed hot water storage\r\ntank. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">System boilers are fed with cold water directly from the\r\nmains, this water is then heated in the boiler and then it’s transferred into a\r\nsealed hot water tank to use when needed, perfect for those who require instant\r\nhot water. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you have room for a hot water tank in your home, then a system boiler\r\ncould be perfect for you. Meanwhile, if you don’t have the additional space,\r\nthe Potterton Assure range is also available as a combi boiler.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Assure 15kW is suitable for smaller homes with up to 10\r\nradiators and a bathroom. If your home requires a higher demand, the Assure\r\n18kW or 24kW are available.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 8, 107, NULL, 'https://www.potterton.co.uk/-/media/websites/pottertonuk/files/assure-system/potterton_assure_system_specsheet_final.pdf?la=en&hash=A05A7B6CE1CCEBAB7AC93EC38836BC85BC41B8A5', '1', '15', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 285mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '93', 15, '70', '<ul><li>A central flue, making installation easier and faster</li><li>Optional outdoor weather sensor</li><li>Built-in drip tray to protect against water ingress</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-life weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li></ul>', 'finish_1623843278.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Assure 15kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Assure 15kW System Gas Boiler.  Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 11:34:38', '2021-07-15 11:22:34'),
(284, 'Potterton Assure 18kW System Gas Boiler', 'potterton-assure-18kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure 18kW system gas boiler is a highly\r\nreliable boiler, with an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for\r\ncentral heating, which can not only help you to reduce your carbon footprint\r\nbut can also help to lower your energy bills.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is important to note when purchasing a new or replacement\r\nsystem boiler, that although the boiler unit itself is compact, you will need\r\nto have space for an additional sealed hot water storage tank which requires\r\nmore room in your home. This is because system boilers are fed with cold water\r\ndirectly from the mains, this water is then heated in the boiler and then it’s\r\ntransferred into a sealed hot water tank to use when needed, which is perfect\r\nfor those who require instant hot water. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">If space is not an issue in your home, then a system boiler\r\ncould be a great option for you. However, if you do not have the room in your\r\nhome, then the Potterton Assure range is available as a combi boiler which is best suited to homes with limited\r\nspace.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure 18kW is one of the more powerful system\r\nboilers in its range, with the ability to heat a home with up to 15 radiators\r\nand a bathroom. The Assure 24kW is available for those with higher demand, but\r\nalso the 12kW and 15kW are available for homes with lesser demand for central\r\nheating and hot water. The Potterton Assure system 18kW and 24kW are also both available as an LPG boiler.</p>', 2, 8, 107, NULL, 'https://www.potterton.co.uk/-/media/websites/pottertonuk/files/assure-system/potterton_assure_system_specsheet_final.pdf?la=en&hash=A05A7B6CE1CCEBAB7AC93EC38836BC85BC41B8A5', '1', '18', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 285mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '93', 18, '70', '<ul><li>A central flue, making installation easier and faster</li><li>Optional outdoor weather sensor</li><li>Built-in drip tray to protect against water ingress</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-life weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li></ul>', 'finish_1623844334.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Assure 18kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Assure 18kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 11:52:14', '2021-07-15 11:24:32'),
(285, 'Potterton Assure 24kW System Gas Boiler', 'potterton-assure-24kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure 24kW is the most powerful system boiler\r\nin its range, with an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for central\r\nheating, meaning that this boiler could potentially help you to reduce your\r\ncarbon footprint and your energy bills.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">When purchasing a new or replacement system boiler, it is\r\nimportant to note that although the boiler unit itself is compact, you will\r\nneed to have space for an additional sealed hot water storage tank in your home. These are often installed in an airing cupboard of a property.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">You will need this additional tank because system boilers are supplied with cold water\r\ndirectly from the mains, they then heat the water in the boiler unit, once it\r\nreaches optimum temperature, it is then moved into a sealed hot water tank to\r\nuse when needed, which is perfect for those who require instant hot water. If\r\nyour home has plenty of space then a system boiler could be a great option for\r\nyou. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure is also available in a combi regular\r\nboiler, and the Assure system 18kW and 24kW are also both available as an LPG\r\nboiler. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">As mentioned, the Potterton Assure 24kW is the most powerful\r\nsystem boilers in its range, with the ability to heat a home with up to 15\r\nradiators and a bathroom. Meanwhile, many homes do not require this demand for\r\ncentral heating and hot water, in this case, the 12kW, 15kW or 18kW may be more\r\nsuitable for your home.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 8, 107, NULL, 'https://www.potterton.co.uk/-/media/websites/pottertonuk/files/assure-system/potterton_assure_system_specsheet_final.pdf?la=en&hash=A05A7B6CE1CCEBAB7AC93EC38836BC85BC41B8A5', '1', '24', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 285mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '93', 24, '70', '<ul><li>A central flue, making installation easier and faster</li><li>Optional outdoor weather sensor</li><li>Built-in drip tray to protect against water ingress</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-life weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li></ul>', 'finish_1623845346.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Assure 24kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Assure 24kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 12:09:06', '2021-07-15 11:25:31');
