(286, 'Potterton Gold 18kW System Gas Boiler', 'potterton-gold-18kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Gold 18kW System is a highly reliable system\r\ngas boiler with an efficiency rating of 89% and an ErP A-rating for central\r\nheating. With these ratings, this system boiler could potentially help you to\r\nreduce not only your carbon footprint but also help to reduce your energy\r\nbills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">A system boiler is ideal for those who have a high demand for\r\ninstant hot water. However, it is important to remember when buying a new or\r\nreplacement system boiler, that you will need to accommodate for an additional\r\nhot water storage tank. </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Although the boiler unit itself is compact and\r\nlightweight, if you have a smaller home with limited space, a system boiler may\r\nnot be the best option for you. However, if the Potterton Gold is the boiler\r\nyou desire, it is also available as a combi boiler for those with limited space. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Gold 18kW is the least powerful system boiler\r\nin its range, however, don’t let this put you off as it is perfect for homes\r\nwith up to 15 radiators and a bathroom. If the Gold 18kW is not\r\npowerful enough to heat your home, the Gold 24kW and 28kW are also available.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 8, 108, NULL, 'https://baxi-public.partsarena.com/Documents/Document?manufacturerId=235&productType=Boiler&productRange=Gold%20ErP&modelId=11249&documentId=3875&documentName=Potterton%20Gold%20System%20ErP%2018%2C24%2C28%20Installation%20(7647623-02)%20Serial%20no%20Ending%20BC', '1', '18', 'H: 780mm, W: 450mm, D: 345mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '89', 18, '70', '<ul><li>Pre-plumbing jig for faster installation&nbsp;</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-life wei