(296, 'Potterton Ultra System 18kW Gas Boiler', 'potterton-ultra-system-18kw-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an efficiency rating of 89% and an ErP A-rating for\r\nboth heating and hot water, the Potterton Ultra System 18kW boiler could help\r\nyou to reduce not only your carbon footprint but also help you to lower your\r\nenergy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nPotterton Ultra System 18kW boiler is known for being a highly reliable gas\r\nboiler with a compact and lightweight design. This system boiler can be fitted into the space of your standard\r\nkitchen cupboard, out of sight, out of mind. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">When purchasing a new or replacement system boiler, it is\r\nimportant to note that you will need an additional hot water storage tank,\r\nwhich is typically located in your airing cupboard. <span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">If you have a smaller home with limited space, a system\r\nboiler may not be the best option, however, Potterton also has many combi boilers\r\nthat may be better suited to your home. If space is not an issue in\r\nyour home and you require instant hot water, then the Ultra system boilers might be a\r\nperfect choice for you. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Ultra 18kW is middle of the range regarding output power\r\nin this range, however, it is the ideal choice if you have a home with up to 15\r\nradiators and one bathroom. On the other hand, if you are looking for a system\r\nboiler that can meet higher demands for central heating and hot water, the\r\nUltra System 21kW or 24kW are available. For homes with lesser demand, the 12kW\r\nand 15kW are also available.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 8, 110, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/potterton/Potterton_Ultra_System_compressed.pdf', '1', '18', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 300mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '89', 18, '70', '<ul><li>Front access for easy installation and future servicing&nbsp;</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-lift weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li><li>Easy to read display screen&nbsp; &nbsp;</li><li>Fully modulating and highly efficient box solution&nbsp;</li><li>Compatible with the Megaflo eco solar cylinder</li></ul>', 'finish_1623852958.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Ultra System 18kW Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Ultra System 18kW Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 14:15:58', '2021-07-15 08:28:41'),
(297, 'Potterton Ultra System 21kW Gas Boiler', 'potterton-ultra-system-21kw-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Ultra 21kW is a highly reliable system gas\r\nboiler that has been designed so that it can be wall-mounted into your standard\r\nkitchen cupboard, out of sight, out of mind. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">When purchasing a new or replacement system boiler it is\r\nimportant to note that you will need to accommodate for an additional hot water\r\nstorage tank. This is because system boilers are fed cold water directly from\r\nthe mains and then the water is heated and transferred into a sealed hot water\r\ntank for when you need it. This will require more space in your home,\r\ntherefore, a system boiler is not recommended for homes with limited space.\r\nHowever, if space is not limited in your home and you have a high demand for\r\ninstant hot water, a system boiler could be perfect for you. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Ultra System 21kW is one of the more powerful\r\nsystem boilers in this range, with the ability to heat a medium-sized home with\r\nup to 15 radiators and a bathroom. The Ultra range has 5 boilers with outputs\r\nof between 12kW and 24kW, so if you feel that your home has a higher\r\ndemand for heating and hot water, the 24kW is available. However, if your home\r\nhas lesser demand, the 12kW, 15kW, or 18kW could be better suited for your home.<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 8, 110, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/potterton/Potterton_Ultra_System_compressed.pdf', '1', '21', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 300mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '89', 21, '70', '<ul><li>Front access for easy installation and future servicing&nbsp;</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-lift weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li><li>Easy to read display screen&nbsp; &nbsp;</li><li>Fully modulating and highly efficient box solution&nbsp;</li><li>Compatible with the Megaflo eco solar cylinder</li></ul>', 'finish_1623853150.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Ultra System 21kW Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Ultra System 21kW Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 14:19:10', '2021-07-21 11:56:55'),
(298, 'Potterton Ultra System 24kW Gas Boiler', 'potterton-ultra-system-24kw-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Ultra 24kW is a highly reliable system gas\r\nboiler that has been designed so that it can be wall-mounted into your standard\r\nkitchen cupboard, out of sight, out of mind.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Thanks to\r\nits high-efficiency rating of 89% and an ErP A-rating for heating, this system\r\nboiler could potentially help you reduce your carbon footprint, as well as help\r\nto lower your energy bills. </span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is important to note when purchasing a new or replacement\r\nsystem boiler that you will need to accommodate for an additional hot water\r\nstorage tank which requires more space in your home. This is because system\r\nboilers are fed cold water directly from the mains and then the water is heated\r\nand transferred into a sealed hot water tank for when you need it. However, if\r\nspace is not limited in your home and you require a high demand for instant hot\r\nwater, a system boiler could be perfect for you. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">This system boiler is the most powerful in its range, with\r\nan output of 24kW for central heating. This is ideal for homes with up to 15\r\nradiators and 1-2 bathrooms. Many smaller homes will not require the output of\r\nthis Ultra System 24kW. In this case, the 12kW, 15kW, 18kW or 21kW could be\r\nbetter suited to your home.</p>', 2, 8, 110, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/potterton/Potterton_Ultra_System_compressed.pdf', '1', '24', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 300mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '89', 24, '70', '<ul><li>Front access for easy installation and future servicing&nbsp;</li><li>Compact design&nbsp;</li><li>Low-lift weight&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Flue options for flexibility during installation</li><li>Easy to read display screen&nbsp; &nbsp;</li><li>Fully modulating and highly efficient box solution&nbsp;</li><li>Compatible with the Megaflo eco solar cylinder</li></ul>', 'finish_1623853311.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Potterton is a good boiler brand that has a good\r\nreliability record and a good customer score. Engineers rate it well across the\r\nboard too. Overall Potterton gets a Which? brand score of 70%, which puts it in\r\na high quality tier of brands that sit just below our Best Buy cut off.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Potterton Ultra System 24kW Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Potterton Ultra System 24kW Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 14:21:51', '2021-07-21 11:58:39'),
(299, 'Vaillant EcoFIT Pure 825 Combi Gas Boiler', 'vaillant-ecofit-pure-825-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">With an efficiency rating of 94% an ErP A-rating and a\r\nflow rate of 10.4 litres per minute, this Vaillant EcoFit Pure 825 Combi gas\r\nboiler is understandably known for its efficiency.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Combi boilers are ideal for smaller homes as they work\r\nas both a water heater and a central heating boiler, wrapped into one\r\ncost-effective unit. Combi boilers remove the need for any additional hot water\r\ncylinder or cold water tanks, meaning they can be installed neatly in your\r\nstandard kitchen cupboard.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p>The Vaillant EcoFit Pure 825 combi boiler has a\r\ncentral heating output rating of 19.1kW, which is perfect for smaller homes\r\nwith up to 10-15 radiators. It also has a hot water output of 25.2kW, ideal for\r\nhomes with a single bathroom. The EcoFit Pure 825 is the least powerful in its\r\nrange, therefore, if you feel that your home has a higher demand for\r\nheating and hot water, the EcoFit Pure 830 and 835 are also available.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 4, 111, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/vaillant/ecofit-pure-combi-install-manual-876620.pdf', '1', '25', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 295mm', '10.4', 'A', '2', '94', 25, '80', '<ul><li>LED display for easy reading</li><li>Front access to the boiler for future maintenance or servicing</li><li>High specification aluminium heat exchanger</li><li>An industry-leading flue length of 10mm</li><li>Compatibility with the Vaillant Smart Controls</li><li>A 4 sided cooling and agitation of the heat exchanger</li></ul>', 'finish_1623854799.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vaillant consistently scores well in the Which? annual boiler\r\nsurvey and this year is no exception. Vaillant has a five-star customer score,\r\na good reliability record and the glowing praise of respected Which? Trusted\r\nTraders heating engineers. Vaillant is the best gas boiler brand of any\r\nincluded in the Which? survey this year, which makes it a Best Buy. We think Vaillant\r\nis great and definitely a good choice of boiler for your home.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vaillant EcoFIT Pure 825 Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vaillant EcoFIT Pure 825 Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-16 14:46:39', '2021-07-21 12:15:07');
