(310, 'Vaillant EcoTEC Pro 24 Combi Gas Boiler', 'vaillant-ecotec-pro-24-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Vaillant EcoTec Pro 24 is a wall-mountable condensing\r\ncombi boiler, with a high-efficiency rating of 94% and ErP A-rating, which\r\ncould potentially help you lower your energy bills.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The word ‘combi’ refers to the fact that this model is\r\na combination boiler, which means it has two separate output ratings, one for\r\ncentral heating and one for domestic hot water. The EcoTec Pro 24 has a\r\ncentral heating output of 24.8W, and a DHW output of 23.4kW, making it perfect\r\nfor properties with up to 15 radiators and a bathroom.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The EcoTec Pro 24 is the least powerful in its range, therefore, if you feel that your home has a high demand for central heating and hot\r\nwater, then the EcoTec Pro is also available in a 28kW, and a 30kW for hot water.</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom