(312, 'Potterton Assure 36kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'potterton-assure-36kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Potterton Assure 36kW is a highly efficient combi gas boiler\r\nwith a high-efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for heating and\r\nhot water. As a result of these ratings, this combi boiler could potentially\r\nhelp you to reduce both your carbon footprint and your energy bills.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p><br></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nPotterton Assure 36kW is the most powerful combi boiler in its range, with an\r\noutput of 36kW for central heating, perfect for heating a larger home with up\r\nto 20 radiators and 2 bathrooms. Many homes will not require this output for\r\ncentral heating and hot water, in this case, the 25kW or 30kW may be better\r\nsuited to your home.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are ideal for smaller homes with limited space, this is because they remove the need for any additional hot or cold water tanks, as you would need with a system or regular boiler.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 8, 97, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/potterton/Assure_Combi_Manual_compressed.pdf', '1', '36', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 285mm', '15', 'A', '2