(327, 'Vaillant EcoFIT Pure 612 System Gas Boiler', 'vaillant-ecofit-pure-612-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nVaillant EcoFit Pure 612 is a reliable system gas boiler with an output rating\r\nof 12.3kW making it well suited to smaller properties with up to 10 radiators.\r\nThanks to its efficiency rating of 94% and ErP A-rating for heating and hot\r\nwater, depending on your current boiler\'s efficiency rating, this system boiler could help you to reduce your energy bills.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">System\r\nboilers are great for those who require hot water on demand. This is because a\r\nsystem boiler has an additional hot water cylinder that stores the heated water supplied from the mains. It is important to note that you will need to\r\naccommodate this extra cylinder when purchasing a new or\r\nreplacement system boiler.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nEcoFit Pure 612 is the least powerful of its range, with an output of 12.3kW.\r\nIf your home has a higher demand for heating and hot water, don’t panic,\r\nVaillant has designed the EcoFit Put 615, 618, 625, and 630, which have outputs between 15kW and 30kW.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 4, 117, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/vaillant/ecoFITpure2.pdf', '1', '12', 'H: 700mm, W: 390mm, D: 295mm', 'N/A', 'A', '2', '94', 12, '80', '<ul><li>Built-in two-stage frost protection</li><li>Compact and lightweight</li><li>Top and rear flue options</li><li>Aluminium heat exchanger&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>An LED digital display screen</li><li>Compatibility with Vaillant controls&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1623935438.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vaillant\r\nconsistently scores well in the Which? annual boiler survey and this year is no\r\nexception. Vaillant has a five-star customer score, a good reliability record\r\nand the glowing praise of respected Which? Trusted Traders heating engineers.\r\nVaillant is the best gas boiler brand of any included in the Which? survey this year,\r\nwhich makes it a Best Buy. We think Vaillant is great and definitely a good\r\nchoice of boiler for your home.<font color=\"#000000\"><o:p></o:p></font></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vaillant EcoFIT Pure 612 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vaillant EcoFIT Pure 612 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-17 13:10:38', '2021-07-16 09:04:08'),
