(332, 'Vaillant EcoTEC Green iQ 627 System Gas Boiler', 'vaillant-ecotec-exclusive-green-iq-627-system-gas-boiler', '<div style=\"mso-element:para-border-div;border-left:windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nborder-right:windowtext 1.0pt;border-style:none;mso-border-left-alt:none windowtext 0cm;\r\nmso-border-right-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm 1.0pt 0cm 1.0pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;mso-border-right-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 1.0pt 0cm 1.0pt\">The Vaillant EcoTec Exclusive Green iQ range is the first-ever boiler with the power of Green iQ technology. The range consists of two high kW output combi boilers with extra condensate technology alongside the EcoTec Green iQ 627 system boiler.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;mso-border-right-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 1.0pt 0cm 1.0pt\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;mso-border-right-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 1.0pt 0cm 1.0pt\">Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of\r\n94% and an ErP A-rating for heat, the EcoTec Exclusive iQ 627 range is known\r\nfor its reliability and efficiency. Thanks to these ratings, this system boiler could help reduce your energy bills, depending on your current boiler\'s efficiency rating.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;mso-border-right-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 1.0pt 0cm 1.0pt\">The EcoTec Exclusive iQ 627 has an output rating of\r\n26.7kW for central heating. This is powerful enough to heat a property with between 15 and 20\r\nradiators.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:6.0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-a