(340, 'Vaillant EcoTEC Plus 48kW System Gas Boiler', 'vaillant-ecotec-plus-48kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nVaillant EcoTec Plus 48kW system gas boiler has a central heating rating of\r\n48kW, which is perfect for large properties with multiple bathrooms and a very\r\nhigh demand for heating and hot water.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></span>This\r\nreliable system boiler has an efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A+ rating for\r\ncentral heating.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The EcoTec Plus 48kW has been designed to be compact for easy\r\ninstallation into a standard kitchen cupboard. It is important to note\r\nthat when buying a new or replacement system boiler, you will need\r\nto accommodate an additional hot water cylinder. This is\r\nbecause system boilers get their water supply directly from the mains, which is\r\nthen heated and stored in this hot water cylinder, ready for when you need it.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span s