(343, 'Vokera Compact 25A Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-compact-25a-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Compact 25A combi gas boiler is ideal for smaller\r\nhomes with limited space. This is because combi boilers remove the need for any\r\nadditional cold water tanks or hot water cylinders. Thanks to its compact and\r\nlightweight design, a combi boiler can be installed inside a standard kitchen\r\ncupboard, out of sight, out of mind (depending on the model).<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Compact 25A has an efficiency rating of 90% and\r\nan ErP A-rating for heating and hot water. Thanks to these ratings, this combi\r\nboiler can help to reduce your\r\ncarbon footprint and potentially lower your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Compact A range has two models with outputs of\r\n25kW and also 29kW. This combi boiler is ideal for small to medium-sized homes with up to 15 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. However, if you feel that your\r\nhome has a higher demand for heating and hot water, the Compact 29A may be\r\nbetter suited to your home\'s needs.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 124, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Vokera/Compact-A.pdf', '1', '25', 'H: 715mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', '10.2', 'A', '5', '90', 25, '46', '<ul><li>Easy to read pressure gauge&nbsp;</li><li>LED digital screen for maximum control and comfort</li><li>A heating and hot water temperature selector</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>User-friendly controls&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624006843.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vokera\r\nboilers have a good reliability record, but its customers aren’t particularly\r\nfond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate other brands higher too. The\r\noverall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%, which is below average.&nbsp;<font color=\"#000000\"><o:p></o:p></font></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Compact 25A Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Compact 25A Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 09:00:43', '2021-07-20 13:50:35'),
(344, 'Vokera Compact 29A Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-compact-29a-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>The Vokera Compact 29A combi gas boiler is ideal for smaller\r\nhomes with limited space. This is because combi boilers remove the need for any\r\nadditional cold water tanks or hot water cylinders. Thanks to its compact and\r\nlightweight design, a combi boiler can be installed inside a standard kitchen\r\ncupboard, out of sight, out of mind.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Compact 29A has an efficiency rating of 90% and\r\nan ErP A rating for heating and hot water. Thanks to these ratings, this combi\r\nboiler is not only known for its reliability but can also help to reduce your\r\ncarbon footprint and potentially lower your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Compact A range has two models with outputs of\r\n25kW and also 29kW. As mentioned, this particular model of combi boiler has an\r\noutput of 29kW for central heating and hot water. This boiler is ideal for a\r\nsmall to medium-sized home with up to 20 radiators and 1 bathroom. Smaller\r\nhomes may not require this demand for central heating and hot water, in this\r\ncase, the Compact 25A may be better suited to your homes’ needs.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 124, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Vokera/Compact-A.pdf', '1', '29', 'H: 715mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', '11.9', 'A', '5', '90', 29, '46', '<ul><li>Easy to read pressure gauge&nbsp;</li><li>LED digital screen for maximum control and comfort</li><li>A heating and hot water temperature selector</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>User-friendly controls&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624007119.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vokera\r\nboilers have a good reliability record, but its customers aren’t particularly\r\nfond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate other brands higher too. The\r\noverall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%, which is below average.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Compact 29A Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Compact 29A Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 09:05:19', '2021-07-20 13:16:48'),
(345, 'Vokera Easi-Heat Plus 25Ci Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-easi-heat-plus-25ci-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Easi-Heat Plus 25Ci is a compact and lightweight\r\ncombination gas boiler that can be installed neatly into your standard kitchen\r\ncupboard. With an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for heating and\r\nhot water, this combi boiler model could help you to save money on your energy\r\nbills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With a combi boiler, water is supplied directly from the\r\nmains supply and then heated and distributed to your\r\ntaps and radiators. No need for storage tanks that take up lots of space in your home.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<br></o:p>The Vokera Easi-Heat Plus range includes 3 combi boilers\r\nwith outputs of 25kW, 29kW, and 32kW. Although the 25Ci, is\r\nthe least powerful in its range, it is powerful enough to heat a home with up\r\nto 15 radiators and one bathroom.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 125, NULL, 'https://www.vokeraeasiheat.co.uk/brochure/EasiHeatPlus.pdf', '1', '25', 'H: 795mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', '10.2', 'A', '5', '93', 25, '46', '<ul><li>Built-in digital clock&nbsp;</li><li>Error code display screen</li><li>User-friendly controls&nbsp;</li><li>Pleated heat exchanger, reducing the risk of scaling</li><li>Anti-cycling controls</li><li>LED digital screen for maximum control and comfort&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624007372.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vokera\r\nboilers have a good reliability record, but its customers aren’t particularly\r\nfond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate other brands higher too. The\r\noverall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%, which is below average.&nbsp;<font color=\"#000000\"><o:p></o:p></font></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Easi-Heat Plus 25Ci Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Easi-Heat Plus 25Ci Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 09:09:32', '2021-07-19 12:40:58'),
(346, 'Vokera Evolve C 24kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-c-24kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve C is a highly reliable combi gas boiler\r\nwith a high-efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP\r\nA-rating for heating and hot water. With these ratings, this combi boiler could\r\nhelp to reduce your carbon footprint and your energy bills. What more could you\r\nask for!<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are often the recommended choice for smaller\r\nproperties with limited space. This is because a combi boiler doesn\'t require a hot water storage cylinder or cold water storage tanks.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve combi gas boilers have five outputs\r\nranging from 24kW to 42kW. This particular model, the C24 is the least powerful of its\r\nrange, with an output of 24kW. However, don’t let this put you off as this\r\ncombi boiler is powerful enough to heat a home with between 10 and 15\r\nradiators, ideal for smaller homes. If you have a slightly larger\r\nhome with a higher demand for central heating and hot water, the Vokera Evolve\r\nC28, C32, C35, and C42 are also available.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve range is also available as a system\r\nboiler, so there is an option for everyone.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 126, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/vokera/EVOLVE.pdf', '1', '24', 'H: 740mm, W: 420mm, D: 275mm', '10.7', 'A', '10', '94', 24, '46', '<ul><li>Fully backlit LCD digital display screen for easy use</li><li>Easy to use controls&nbsp;</li><li>Clock timer</li><li>Text-driven menus</li><li>Built-in CO2 monitor</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>An aluminium heat exchanger</li><li>Safety valve for maximum comfort i