(351, 'Vokera Evolve C 32kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-c-32kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are ideal for smaller homes with limited\r\nspace, this is because they don’t need any additional hot water cylinders or\r\ncold water tanks as you would with a system or regular boiler. Combi boilers\r\nare designed with both the water heater and central heating unit all in one, resulting in them being compact and lightweight, so they can be installed\r\ninto a standard kitchen cupboard. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve C32 has a high-efficiency rating of 94%\r\nand had an ErP A-rating for both central heating and hot water. With these\r\nratings, this combi boiler can help to reduce your carbon footprint and your\r\nenergy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an output of 32kW, the C32 is ideal for medium-sized\r\nhomes that don’t have an excessive need for heating and hot water but have up\r\nto 20 radiators. The C32 is mid-range when it comes to output in this range.\r\nThe C35 and C42 combi boilers are available for those with a higher demand for\r\nheating and hot water, meanwhile, the C24 and C28 are also available for\r\nsmaller homes with less demand. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The Vokera\r\nEvolve range is also available as a system boiler, so there is an option for\r\neveryone.&nbsp;&nbsp;<