(353, 'Vokera Evolve C 42kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-c-42kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve C42 is the most powerful of its range,\r\nwith an output of 42kW, powerful enough to heat a larger home with up to 20\r\nradiators and two bathrooms. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are often the preferred choice of boiler types due to\r\ntheir compact and lightweight design allowing them to be installed without the\r\nneed for any additional hot or cold water tanks that would be needed for a\r\nsystem or regular gas boiler.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A-rating for\r\nheating and hot water, the Vokera Evolve C42 could potentially help you to\r\nreduce your carbon footprint and your energy bills. depending on your current boilers efficiency rating.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">As mentioned, the Vokera Evolve C42 is the most powerful boiler in its\r\nrange, with an output of 42kW. Although this output is great for larger homes,\r\nsmall and medium-sized homes would not need this boiler. If your home has a\r\nlesser demand for heating and hot water, or simply has less than 20 radiators,\r\nthe Vokera Evolve C24, C28, C32 or C36 combi boilers may be better suited to your home. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">