(354, 'Vokera Excel 25 Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-excel-25-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Excel 25 is a lightweight and compact combi gas\r\nboiler that can be neatly installed inside your standard kitchen cupboard, out\r\nof sight, out of mind. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to its efficiency rating of 92% and an ErP A-rating\r\nfor both central heating and hot water, this sleek combi boiler could not only\r\nhelp you to lower your carbon footprint but also help you to lower your energy\r\nbills.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Excel range has two outputs, the 25kW and the\r\n29kW. This particular model, the 25kW is ideal for homes with moderate demand\r\nfor central heating and hot water. The Vokera Excel 25 can comfortably heat a\r\nhome with up to 15 radiators and a bathroom. If your home has a slightly higher demand, then the 29kW may\r\nbe a better option for your home.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 127, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/vokera/excel_1.pdf', '1', '25', 'H: 715mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', '10.2', 'A', '5', '92', 25, '46', '<ul><li>Fully backlit LCD digital display screen for easy use</li><li>Easy to use controls&nbsp;</li><li>Clock timer</li><li>Text-driven menus</li><li>Built-in CO2 monitor</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>An aluminium heat exchanger</li><li>Safety valve for maximum comfort in your home</li><li>Attach the optional RF wireless combined room thermostat</li></ul>', 'finish_1624011137.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vokera\r\nboilers have a good reliability record, but its customers aren’t particularly\r\nfond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate other brands higher too. The\r\noverall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%, which is below average.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Excel 25 Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know abou