(355, 'Vokera Excel 29kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-excel-29-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are ideal for homes with limited space. This\r\nis because they remove the need for any additional hot or cold water tanks as\r\nyou would need for a system or regular boiler. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Excel 29 is a great, lightweight, and compact\r\ncombi gas boiler that can be neatly installed inside your standard kitchen\r\ncupboard, out of sight, out of mind.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to its efficiency rating of 92% and an ErP A-rating\r\nfor both central heating and hot water, this sleek combi boiler could not only\r\nhelp you to lower your carbon footprint but also help you to lower your energy\r\nbills.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Excel 29 combi boiler is the most powerful of its range, with\r\nan output of 29kW. This combi boiler is perfect for heating a home with up to\r\n20 radiators and a bathroom. The Vokera Excel range has two kW output models, the 25kW and the 29kW. If you feel that your home has a\r\nlower demand for central heating and hot water, the Excel 25kW combi boiler may be a better\r\noption for your home.<o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 127, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/vokera/excel_1.pdf', '1', '29', 'H: 715mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', '12.1', 'A', '5', '92', 29, '46', '<ul><li>Fully backlit LCD digital display screen for easy use</li><li>Easy to use controls&nbsp;</li><li>Clock timer</li><li>Text-driven menus</li><li>Built-in CO2 monitor</li><li>Built-in frost protection for extra peace of mind during the colder months&nbsp;</li><li>An aluminium heat exchanger</li><li>Safety valve for maximum comfort in your home</li><li>Attach the optional RF