(356, 'Vokera Linea One 38kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-linea-one-38kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Linea One 38kW Combi Gas Boiler is powerful enough\r\nto heat a home with up to 20 radiators and 2 bathrooms. The combi\r\nboiler itself is compact and lightweight; meaning that it can be installed\r\nneatly into a standard kitchen cupboard, but it still packs a punch, perfect for homes\r\nwith a very high demand for heating and hot water. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP\r\nA-rating, this combi boiler could also help you to reduce your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are perfect for smaller-sized homes with\r\nlimited space. This is because combi boilers have a water heater and central\r\nheating unit fitted into one single unit, meaning that the heated water can be sent\r\ndirectly to your taps and radiators when needed. Combi boilers also remove the\r\nneed for any additional cold water tanks or hot water cylinders, as you would\r\nwith a system or regular boiler.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 128, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Vokera/linea_one_end_user_manual.pdf', '1', '38', 'H: 845mm, W: 453mm, D: 358mm', '15.6', 'A', '5', '93', 38, '46', '<ul><li>A weather compensation control</li><li>Modulation ratio of 10:1 which maximises efficiency and comfort</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection for extra peace of mind during the colder months</li><li>An anti-seize function that protects the pump&nbsp;</li><li>Self-start program to help increase efficiency</li></ul>', 'finish_1624012331.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vokera\r\nboilers have a good reliability record, but its customers aren’t particularly\r\nfond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate other brands higher too. The\r\noverall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%, which is below average.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Linea One 38kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Linea One 38kW Combi Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 10:32:11', '2021-07-19 12:34:23'),
(357, 'Vokera Unica i28kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'vokera-unica-i28kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Unica i28kW combi gas boiler is a condensing\r\nboiler can be easily wall-mounted and installed neatly inside a standard\r\nkitchen cupboard, thanks to its low lift weight and compact design.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Combi boilers are often the preferred boiler choice because\r\nthey remove the need for any additional hot water cylinders or cold water tanks as the water heater and the central heating is built into one single unit.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 89.6% and an ErP\r\nA-rating for both central heating and hot water, this boiler could not only\r\nhelp you to reduce your energy bills but could also help reduce your carbon\r\nfootprint. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Unica ‘i’ range has 3 combi boilers with outputs\r\nof 28kW, 32kW, and 36kW. The i28 is the least powerful combi boiler in its\r\nrange, however, with an output of 28kW, it is still powerful enough to heat\r\nsmall to medium-sized properties with up to 15 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. However, if you feel\r\nthat your home has a higher demand for central heating and hot water, the\r\ni32 or i36 may be more suitable.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 1, 10, 129, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/User_Manuals/Vokera/ulcia_28x.pdf', '1', '28', 'H: 780mm, W: 400mm, D: 358mm', '11.5', 'A', '5', '89', 28, '46', '<ul><li>Easy to read and see pressure gauge</li><li>A clear display screen</li><li>A heating and hot water temperature selector</li><li>A heat exchanger with patented technology</li><li>Automatic self-start programme&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protecti