(367, 'Vokera Evolve S 18kW System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-s-18kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve S 18kW is known for being a reliable\r\nsystem gas boiler thanks to its high-efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP\r\nA-rating for heat. These ratings help to reduce not only your carbon footprint\r\nbut also your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">When purchasing a new or\r\nreplacement system boiler, you will need to make room for an additional hot\r\nwater storage cylinder. With system boilers, most of the important parts of the\r\nhot water and heating system, including the pump and the expansion vessel, are\r\nbuilt-in to the unit itself, making installation quick and easy.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an output of 18kW for central heating, this model is\r\nthe least powerful in the Evolve S system range, however, it is ideal for\r\nsmaller homes with up to 10 radiators. If you feel that your home requires a\r\nhigher demand for central heating and hot water, then 24kW, 30kW, or 35kW could\r\nbe better suited to your home. As well as a system boiler range, Vokera has\r\ndesigned the Evolve S range in a combi boiler, so there is an option for\r\neveryone.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 10, 134, NULL, 'https://www.vokera.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Vokera_Product_Guide_ED3_0619.pdf', '1', '18', 'H: 740mm, W: 420mm, D: 275mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '94', 18, '46', '<ul><li>Flue options for flexible installation</li><li>ACC combustion to help reduced emissions</li><li>A text-driven menu for easy setup and adjustment</li><li>Modulation ratio of 7:1</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection which will protect your boiler during the colder months</li><li>A self-start program that protects your pump&nbsp;</li><li>Enhanced Autostop disabling function for extra peace of mind</li></ul>', 'finish_1624019640.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 12:34:00', '2021-07-19 11:14:03'),
(368, 'Vokera Evolve S 24kW System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-s-24kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve S 24kW is a reliable system gas boiler\r\nthanks to its high-efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A-rating for heat. These\r\nratings help to reduce not only your carbon footprint but also your energy\r\nbills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Evolve S system boiler range includes 4 different outputs between 18kW and 35kW. This model,\r\nthe 24kW, has an output of 24kW, powerful enough to heat a home with up to 15\r\nradiators and a single bathroom. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">For those who are looking for a system boiler that meets a\r\nhigher demand for central heating and hot water, the 30kW and 35kW are\r\navailable. If your home has less than 15 radiators, then the 18kW system boiler could be better suited to your home. As well as a system boiler range, Vokera\r\nhas designed the Evolve S range as a combi boiler, so there is an option for\r\neveryone. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is important to consider that when purchasing a new or\r\nreplacement system boiler that you will need to make room for an additional hot\r\nwater storage cylinder. System boilers are designed with the pump and the expansion vessel built into the boiler itself.\r\nThis makes installation quick and easy. Although you will need to make\r\nroom for an additional hot water storage cylinder, the boiler itself is compact\r\nand lightweight and can be fitted neatly into your standard kitchen cupboard.<o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 10, 134, NULL, 'https://qr.vokera.co.uk/qr?action=download&key=Generic+Document%7CDoc-0086125%7C0&name=DOCUMENTS%2F19%2F57%2F1957sptrglhwylfusi-hognp-9fht7gk9gd8oenanyp.vx9', '1', '24', 'H: 740mm, W: 420mm, D: 300mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '94', 24, '46', '<ul><li>Flue options for flexible installation</li><li>ACC combustion to help reduced emissions</li><li>A text-driven menu for easy setup and adjustment</li><li>Modulation ratio of 7:1</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>A self-start program that protects your pump&nbsp;</li><li>Enhanced Autostop disabling function&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624019953.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Evolve S 24kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Evolve S 24kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 12:39:13', '2021-07-21 08:18:10'),
(370, 'Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-s-30kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve S 30kW is a wall-mountable condensing\r\nsystem gas boiler, with an efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A-rating. These\r\nratings mean that this system boiler could potentially help you to reduce your\r\ncarbon footprint but also your energy bills. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Evolve S 30kW is a compact and lightweight unit that can\r\nbe installed neatly into a standard kitchen cupboard. However, it is important\r\nto consider that when purchasing a new or replacement system boiler that you\r\nwill need to make room for an additional hot water storage cylinder. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">System boilers are designed with the most important parts\r\nsuch as the pump and the expansion vessel built-in to the boiler itself. This\r\nhelps with making installation quick and easy. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Evolve S 30kW is one of the more powerful system boilers\r\nin its range, with an output of 30kW. This boiler can comfortably heat a home\r\nwith up to 20 radiators. Also, as a system boiler, hot water will be stored in\r\na cylinder, ready for your when needed. The 35kW is also available if your property has a\r\nhigher demand for heating and hot water, however, the 18kW and 24kW are also\r\navailable for those with lesser demand.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 10, 134, NULL, 'https://qr.vokera.co.uk/qr?action=download&key=Generic+Document%7CDoc-0086125%7C0&name=DOCUMENTS%2F19%2F57%2F1957sptrglhwylfusi-hognp-9fht7gk9gd8oenanyp.vx9', '1', '30', 'H: 740mm, W: 420mm, D: 275mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '94', 30, '46', '<ul><li>Flue options for flexible installation</li><li>ACC combustion to help reduced emissions</li><li>A text-driven menu for easy setup and adjustment</li><li>Modulation ratio of 7:1</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li><li>A self-start program that protects your pump&nbsp;</li><li>Enhanced Autostop disabling function&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624020494.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 12:48:14', '2021-07-21 08:19:11'),
(371, 'Vokera Evolve S 35kW System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-evolve-s-30kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Evolve 35kW is the most powerful in its range,\r\nwith an output of 35kW, which is powerful enough to heat a home with up to 20\r\nradiators and 2 bathrooms. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With a high-efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A-rating for\r\nheating and hot water, this system boiler could potentially help to reduce not\r\nonly your carbon footprint but could also help to reduce your energy bills. </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to being lightweight and compact, this system\r\nboiler can be installed into your standard kitchen cupboard, so you don’t have\r\nto worry about it ruining your kitchen aesthetics.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With an output of 35kW, this system boiler is perfect for\r\nmedium-sized homes with a high demand for heating and hot water. For smaller\r\nhomes with lesser demand for heating and hot water, the Vokera Evolve 18kW,\r\n24kW and 30kW are also available. The Evolve S range is also available as a\r\ncombi boiler.&nbsp;<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 10, 134, NULL, 'https://qr.vokera.co.uk/qr?action=download&key=Generic+Document%7CDoc-0086125%7C0&name=DOCUMENTS%2F19%2F57%2F1957sptrglhwylfusi-hognp-9fht7gk9gd8oenanyp.vx9', '1', '35', 'H: 740mm, W: 420mm, D: 275mm', 'N/A', 'A', '7', '94', 35, '46', '<ul><li>Flue options for flexible installation</li><li>ACC combustion to help reduced emissions</li><li>A text-driven menu for easy setup and adjustment</li><li>Modulation ratio of 7:1</li><li>Easy to use controls</li><li>Built-in frost protection which will protect your boiler during the colder months</li><li>A self-start program that protects your pump&nbsp;</li><li>Enhanced Autostop disabling function for extra peace of mind</li></ul>', 'finish_1624021310.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Evolve S 30kW System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 13:01:50', '2021-07-19 11:16:07');
