(374, 'Vokera Mynute i30 System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-mynute-i30-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nVokera Mynute i30 is a newer range of system boiler. Thanks to its efficiency\r\nrating of 89.1% and ErP B-rating for heat, this system boiler&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span>can help reduce your carbon footprint and energy bills if your boiler is older, but there are more efficient boilers available to increase your savings further.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">With a kW output of 30kW, the i30 is the most powerful in its range, perfect for medium\r\nto larger homes with up to 20 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. Many\r\nhomes will not require this output for central heating and hot water. If your\r\nhome has less than 15 radiators or only one bathroom, the Vokera Mynute i20 may\r\nbe better suited to you and your home. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nVokera i30 boiler unit is a compact and lightweight system that can be\r\ninstalled into a standard kitchen cupboard, so you don’t have to worry about it\r\nruining your aesthetics.&nbsp;</span>However,\r\nit is important to note when considering purchasing a new or replacement system\r\nboiler, that you will need to accommodate space for an additional hot water storage\r\ncylinder. For this reason, system boilers are not\r\nrecommended for homes with limited space.&nbsp;</p>', 2, 10, 136, NULL, 'https://www.vokera.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Mynute-i20-i30-installation-and-user-manual.pdf', '1', '30', 'H: 780mm, W: 400mm, D: 338mm', 'N/A', 'A', '5', '89', 30, '46', '<ul><li>Rear flue options for flexibility during installation</li><li>10:1 modulation ratio</li><li>Built-in onboard relay</li><li>Full compatibility with solar thermal</li><li>An OpenTherm embedded</li><li>Easy to use controls for maximum comfort and control in your home</li></ul>', 'finish_1624022690.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Mynute i30 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Mynute i30 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 13:24:50', '2021-07-19 10:57:40'),
(375, 'Vokera Vision 20s System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-vision-20s-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Vision 20s system gas boiler has been designed with the\r\ncustomer in mind. Its compact and lightweight design means that it is perfect\r\nfor smaller homes with limited space, and can be neatly installed into a kitchen\r\ncupboard.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to its efficiency rating of 89% and ErP B-rating, this model of boiler can also help to reduce your energy bills if you have an older, inefficient boiler. However, many newer boilers offer efficiency ratings of up to 96%.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p><br></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Vision 20s has an output of 20kW which is powerful enough to heat a home with up to 15 radiators and a single bathroom. If you believe that your home has a higher demand for central heating and hot water, the Vision 25s is also available with an output of 25kW.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">However, it is important to note that when purchasing a new\r\nor replacement system boiler, you will need to have the room in your home for an\r\nadditional hot water cylinder, which is typically located in an airing cupboard\r\nof a home. For this reason, system boilers are not recommended for homes with\r\nlimited space. On the plus side, the Vokera Vision range is also available as a combi boiler if space is limited in your home.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', 2, 10, 137, NULL, 'https://www.vokera.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/vision-system-20-25-user-installation-and-servicing-manual.pdf', '1', '20', 'H: 715mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', 'N/A', 'A', '5', '89', 20, '46', '<ul><li>Easy to read&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls&nbsp;</li><li>LED digital display screen</li><li>Built-in frost protection for peace of mind&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624024292.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Vision 20s System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Vision 20s System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 13:51:32', '2021-07-19 10:50:25'),
(376, 'Vokera Vision 25s System Gas Boiler', 'vokera-vision-25s-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Vokera Vision 25s system gas boiler has been designed\r\nwith the customer in mind. Its compact and lightweight design means that it can\r\nbe installed nice and neatly into a kitchen cupboard.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks to its efficiency rating of 89.1% and ErP B-rating,\r\nthis system model boiler is not only reliable but can also help to reduce your\r\nenergy bills. The Vokera Vision 25s has an output of 25kW, powerful enough to heat a home with up to 20 radiators and a single bathroom. If you believe that your home has a lesser demand for central heating and hot water, the Vision 20s is also available with an output of 20kW, better suited to homes with 15 radiators.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">It is important to\r\nmake a note that when purchasing a new or replacement system boiler, you\r\nwill need to ensure that your home has the extra space required for an hot water cylinder. These are typically installed in an airing cupboard, or a similar sized space in your home. For this reason, system boilers are not recommended for homes with limited space. However, if a Vokera Vision is the boiler model you want, it is also available as a combi boiler, better suited to smaller homes with less space.&nbsp;</p>', 2, 10, 137, NULL, 'https://www.vokera.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/vision-system-20-25-user-installation-and-servicing-manual.pdf', '1', '25', 'H: 715mm, W: 405mm, D: 248mm', 'N/A', 'A', '5', '89', 25, '46', '<ul><li>Easy to read&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to use controls&nbsp;</li><li>LED digital display screen</li><li>Built-in frost protection for peace of mind&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624024718.jpg', 0, '<p><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">Vokera boilers have a good reliability record, but its\r\ncustomers aren’t particularly fond of their boilers, and heating engineers rate\r\nother brands higher too. The overall Which? score for Vokera boilers is 46%,\r\nwhich is below average.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vokera Vision 25s System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Vokera Vision 25s System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 13:58:38', '2021-07-19 10:52:52'),
(377, 'Viessmann Vitodens 100-W 13kW Regular Gas Boiler', 'viessmann-vitodens-100-w-13kw-regular-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Vitodens 100-W regular boiler range has an efficiency rating of\r\n94% and an ErP A-rating for heat, making this model a reliable regular gas\r\nboiler that could potentially reduce not only your carbon footprint but also\r\nyour energy bills.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Vitodens 100-W regular boiler range includes five models with\r\noutput ratings of between 13kW and 35kW. This particular model is the least\r\npowerful in its range, with an output of 13kW, however, it is ideal for\r\nproperties with up to 10 radiators. If you believe that your home requires a\r\nmore powerful output, then the 16kw, 19kW, 26kW, and 35kW are available.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">It is important to note when considering purchasing a\r\nnew or replacement regular boiler, that you will need to accommodate for an\r\nadditional hot water cylinder (typically located in an airing cupboard or similar size space in your home), as well as a feed and expansion tank, which are\r\ntypically installed in the attic of your home. As a result of this, regular boilers are not\r\nrecommended for properties with limited space such as a flat. On the plus side, the Vitodens 100-W range is also available as a combi boiler for smaller homes.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">If you don\'t already have a\r\nregular boiler installed then a system or combi boiler would be more\r\nappropriate due to the complex pipework needed.&nbsp;<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 3, 5, 146, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/viessmann/Vitodens-100-W-Compact.pdf', '1', '13', 'H: 600mm, W: 375mm, D: 285mm', 'N/A', 'A', '5', '94', 13, '72', '<ul><li>Inox-Radial heat exchanger for maximum efficiency</li><li>Combined PRV and condense connection</li><li>Easy to use and read display screen&nbsp;</li><li>User-friendly controls&nbsp;</li><li>Built-in frost protection&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1624028474.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Viessmann\r\nboilers have been Best Buys for the past few years, but they just miss out this\r\nyear. Viessmann still makes great boilers that are reliable and loved by people\r\nwho own them. Heating engineers rate them too, just not quite as highly as the\r\nvery very best, so they narrowly miss out on a Best Buy.<font color=\"#000000\"><o:p></o:p></font></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Viessmann Vitodens 100-W 13kW Regular Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Viessmann Vitodens 100-W 13kW Regular Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-06-18 15:01:14', '2021-07-16 13:5