(402, 'Worcester Bosch Greenstar 2000 25kW Combi Gas Boiler', 'worcester-bosch-greenstar-2000-25kw-combi-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Worcester Bosch is known for being one of the most reliable gas boiler brands on the market. The Worcester Bosch Greenstar 2000 25kW is also named one of\r\nthe quietest combi gas boilers on the market, at 45dB.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">With an efficiency rating of 93% and an ErP A-rating for\r\ncentral heating and hot water, this combi boiler could potentially help you to\r\nreduce your energy bills, depending on your current boiler\'s efficiency rating.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Although the Worcester Bosch Greenstar 2000 25kW is the least powerful in its range,\r\nwith an output of 25kW, it is perfect for small to medium-sized homes with up to 15\r\nradiators and one bathroom. However, for homes with a slightly higher demand for\r\ncentral heating and hot water, the Greenstar 2000 30kW is available and may be\r\nbetter suited to your home. <o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Combi boilers are ideal for properties with limited\r\nspace, as they remove the need for any additional hot or cold water tanks, as you\r\nwould need with a system or regular boiler. Thanks to their compact size and low-