(427, 'Worcester Bosch Greenstar 8000 Life 30kW System Gas Boiler', 'worcester-bosch-greenstar-8000-life-30kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p>The Worcester Bosch Greenstar 8000 Life system gas boiler is the most powerful, wall-hung system in the range, with upgraded designs such as improved controls and wireless connectivity.</p>\r\n<br><p>With an efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A-rating for central heating, this system boiler is not only highly reliable but can also help you reduce your energy usage, lowering your energy bills.</p>\r\n<br><p>The Worcester Bosch 8000 Life 30kW is perfect for larger homes with up to 20 radiators and 1-2 bathrooms. For even larger homes with a higher demand for central heating and hot water, the 35kW is also available.</p>\r\n<br><p>The 8000 Life System gas boiler has been designed to be compact and lightweight, for easy installation into a standard kitchen cupboard. However, it is important to note that you will need an additional hot water storage cylinder installed with a system boiler, which is usually installed in an airing cupboard or a similar size space in your home. Therefore, if space is limited in your home, then a combi boiler may be a better option.&nbsp;</p>', 2, 1, 160, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/worcester_bosh/8000_Life_System_2.pdf', '1', '30', 'H: 780mm, W: 440mm, D: 365mm', 'N/A', 'A', '10', '94', 30, '79', '<ul><li>Upgraded smart technology&nbsp;</li><li>User-friendly navigation controls</li><li>A LCD full-colour display screen</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>Compatibility with the Bosch EasyControls</li><li>Wireless controls</li><li>Ideal for larger homes with more than one bathroom</li></ul>', 'finish_1624364325.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Worcester\r\nBosch is one of the best boiler brands you can buy and well worthy of its\r\nWhich? Best Buy. Its boilers are fantastically reliable, loved by their owners\r\nand well respected by expert heating engineers. The overall Which? sco