(428, 'Worcester Bosch Greenstar 8000 Life 35kW System Gas Boiler', 'worcester-bosch-greenstar-8000-life-35kw-system-gas-boiler', '<p>With an efficiency rating of 94% and an ErP A-rating for central heating, the Worcester Bosch Greenstar 8000 Life 35kW system boiler is not only highly reliable but can also help you reduce your energy levels, lowering your energy bills long term.</p><p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Worcester Bosch 8000 Life 35kW is perfect for larger homes with up to 20 radiators and 2 bathrooms. Many smaller homes do not require this demand for central heating and hot water. In this case, the Worcester Bosch 8000 Life 30kW is available for homes with lesser demand.</p><p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 8000 Life System gas boiler has been designed to be compact and lightweight, for easy installation into a standard kitchen cupboard. However, it is important to note that you will need an additional hot water storage cylinder installed with a system boiler. Hot water cylinders are usually installed in an airing cupboard or a similar size space in your home. Therefore, if space is limited, then a combi boiler may be a better option.&nbsp;</p>', 2, 1, 160, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/worcester_bosh/8000_Life_System_2.pdf', '1', '35', 'H: 780mm, W: 440mm, D: 365mm', 'N/A', 'A', '12', '94', 35, '79', '<ul><li>Upgraded smart technology&nbsp;</li><li>User-friendly navigation controls</li><li>A LCD full-colour display screen</li><li>Built-in frost protection</li><li>Compatibility with the Bosch EasyControls</li><li>Wireless controls</li><li>Ideal for larger homes with more than one bathroom</li></ul>', 'finish_1624364816.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Worcester\r\nBosch is one of the best boiler brands you can buy and well worthy of its\r\nWhich? Best Buy. Its boilers are fantastically reliable, loved by their owners\r\nand well respected by expert heating engineers. The overall Which? score for\r\nWorcester Bosch gas boilers is 79%, which is excel