(460, 'Ideal Vogue Max S15 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-vogue-max-s15-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\nIdeal Vogue Max S15 System gas boiler is a great contender if you’re looking\r\nto purchase a new or replacement system boiler. With an efficiency rating of\r\n92% and an ErP A-rating, the Ideal Vogue Max S15 could potentially help reduce\r\nyour energy bills. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Although\r\nthe Ideal Vogue Max S15 is the least powerful boiler in this range, don’t let\r\nthat put you off as it still packs a punch! If you have a smaller home with around 10 radiators, this\r\nboiler could be perfect for you. </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">If you are looking for a\r\nmore powerful boiler, the Ideal Vogue Max range offers the S18, which is 18kW,\r\nthe S26, 26kW and even the S32 which has an output rating of 32kW.<br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">System boilers are ideal for homes with a high demand for instant hot water. This is because syst