(463, 'Ideal Vogue Max S32 System Gas Boiler', 'ideal-vogue-max-s32-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Made in the UK, the Ideal Vogue Max S32 is a system gas boiler known for its reliability and efficiency. Thanks to its rating of\r\n93% and ErP A-rating, this means that this system boiler could\r\nhelp lower your energy bills and carbon footprint. <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Vogue Max S32 is the most powerful system boiler in\r\nits range with an output rating of 32kW, which is powerful enough to heat a\r\nlarger home with up to 20 radiators. <span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Should this boiler be too powerful for your home then the Ideal Vogue\r\nMax range includes three other boilers with lower output ratings. These include\r\ncentral heating outputs of 15kW, 18kW and 26kW.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">System\r\nboilers have separate hot water cylinders. It is important to note that when\r\npurchasing a new or replacement system boiler, you will need to take into\r\nconsideration space for an additional hot water storage cylinder. </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: in