(464, 'Alpha ProTec Plus 50 System Gas Boiler', 'alpha-protec-plus-50-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Alpha ProTec Plus 50 is a highly efficient and\r\nreliable system gas boiler, thanks to its rating of 92% for efficiency and ErP\r\nA-rating for both central heating and hot water. Thanks to these ratings, this system boiler could also help you to lower your energy bills.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Perfectly suited for a larger home with high demand for both hot water and central heating, the ProTec Plus 50 has an\r\noutput reach of 54kW, which is powerful enough to heat a property with up to 20\r\nradiators and two bathrooms with baths. Many homes will not require a higher kW output than this boiler model, however, the ProTec Plus range has outputs that reach 115kW that would be great for large commercial properties.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">System boilers are ideal for those that need instant\r\nhot water, however, it is important to note when purchasing a new or a replacement system boiler, you will need to\r\naccommodate for an additional hot water storage tank. This is because the water\r\nis supplied directly from the mains, heated up, and then stored inside a hot\r\nwater storage tank for when it\'s needed. Due to needing an additional tank, system boilers are not recommended for homes with limited space.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoN