(466, 'Alpha ProTec Plus 90 System Gas Boiler', 'alpha-protec-plus-90-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Alpha ProTec Plus 90 is a system gas boiler\r\ndesigned for larger homes or office space etc. The unit itself has been designed to be\r\ncompact and easy to wall-mount, however, it is slightly larger than your average boiler, measuring over 1m in height.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">It is important to note when purchasing a new or\r\nreplacement system gas boiler, that you will need to accommodate for an\r\nadditional hot water storage tank. This is because the water is supplied\r\ndirectly from the mains, heated up, and then stored inside the hot water storage\r\ntank for when it\'s needed. System gas boilers are ideal for those who need\r\ninstant hot water, however, they are not recommended for smaller homes with\r\nlimited space.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">With an efficiency rating of 92% and an ErP A-rating\r\nfor central heating, the ProTec Plus range is a very reliable system gas boiler\r\nthat could potentially help you reduce your carbon footprint as well as your\r\nenergy bills, depending on the efficiency of your current heating system.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The ProTec Plus 90 is one of the most powerful of the\r\nfour system boilers in its range, with a central heating output of 94kW. Alpha has also designed the ProTec Plus 50 and 70 for properties that do\r\nnot require this high of kW output demand for heating and hot water.&nbsp;<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 2, 11, 48, NULL, 'https://www.freeboilermanuals.com/assets/pdf/alpha/Pro-Tec-Plus-50-70-90-115-Instructions-04-15.pdf', '1', '98', 'H: 1038mm, W: 600mm, D: 632mm', 'N/A', 'A', '5', '92', 98, '45', '<ul><li>A stainless steel heat exchanger</li><li>A 2m long flying mains lead</li><li>An open or concentric push-fit flue system</li><li>Built-in plume management</li><li>Easy access for servicing and built-in commissioning</li><li>Fitted with a fault-finding system for easy diagnoses of any issues</li><li>Easy to use controls&nbsp;</li><li>Easy to read digital screen</li><li>Easy to read pressure gauge&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1626085454.jpg', 0, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Alpha\r\nboilers aren’t up to scratch when compared with other boiler brands on the\r\nmarket. Its reliability is average, as is its customer score. Heating engineers\r\nalso tend to think its average on nearly every metric, other than whether the\r\nengineer is likely to recommend the brand, where Alpha comes out below average.&nbsp;<span style=\"color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Alpha ProTec Plus 90 System Gas Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Alpha ProTec Plus 90 System Gas Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-07-12 10:24:14', '2021-07-21 13:46:07'),
(467, 'Alpha ProTec Plus 115 System Gas Boiler', 'alpha-protec-plus-115-system-gas-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">The Alpha ProTec Plus 115 is a system gas boiler\r\ndesigned for larger homes or commercial properties. With an efficiency rating of 92% and an ErP A-rating\r\nfor central heating, the ProTec Plus range is an efficient system gas boiler\r\nthat could help you to reduce not only your carbon footprint but also help to\r\nlower your energy bills.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">This system gas boiler has been designed to be compact\r\nand easy to wall-mount, however, it is larger than your average boiler, measuring at over 1m in height, therefore would not fit inside your standard kitchen cupboard.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\">Although system gas boilers are ideal for homes that\r\nneed instant hot water, it is important to note when purchasing a new or a replacement system boiler, that you will need to accommodate for an additional\r\nhot water storage tank. This is because the water is supplied directly from the\r\nmains, heated up and then stored inside a hot water storage tank for when it\'s needed.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:\r\n12.0pt;margin-left:0cm\"> <o:p></o:p></p><p>