(469, 'Glow Worm Compact 24kW Combi Boiler', 'glow-worm-compact-24kw-combi-boiler', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The Compact combi range is Glow-worm\'s latest addition to their boiler\r\nfamily. This combi boiler&nbsp;range has been designed to be the most compact and\r\nlightweight boiler that they have produced. However, don’t let its size fool\r\nyou, as this combi boiler delivers a big performance.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">This combi boiler has been designed to be sturdy and\r\nreliable, for extra peace of mind. It is also described as an \'installers dream\' as its size allows for easy, hassle-free installation, not to mention that it\r\ncan also be installed inside your standard kitchen cupboard, out of sight, out\r\nof mind. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background-image: init