for the central heating return&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'finish_1626357948.jpg', 0, '<p>Glow-worm is an average boiler brand. It has an average reliability record and engineers tend to rate it about average too. Customers who own a Glow-worm tend to like it, and engineers report that it’s easy to get hold of parts and spares.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you’re considering this boiler brand, it’s worth checking the Which? best boiler brands page to make sure you get a boiler from one of the best boiler manufacturers around.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Glow Worm Compact 24kW Combi Boiler', 'Everything you need to know about the Glow Worm Compact 24kW Combi Boiler. Including an overview of the boiler, key statistics including dimensions and flow rate, and the boilers review score.', '2021-07-15 14:05:48', '2021-07-19 09:55:53'),
