(46, 'comparison_firstcontainer_kwoutput', '<h2 style=\"font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Searching by kW Output</h2><p>As a general rule, the more heat and hot water you require for your home, the higher the kW boiler you will need.</p><p><br></p><p>You can use the filter below to search for specific kW boiler ranges based on your heating requirements. We’ve written an article on <a href=\"https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/what-size-kw-boiler-do-i-need-to-heat-my-home\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff9c00\"><u>what size kW boiler do I need</u></font></a>? to help you out if you aren’t sure.</p><p><br></p><p>It’s worth noting that if you complete the <a href=\"https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/find-a-boiler\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff9c00\"><u>WarmZilla Survey</u></font></a> to get a boiler quote, our clever system calculates your water and heating requirements and gives you a list of boilers suitable for your home.</p>', NULL, '2021-07-02 08:38:46'),
