(49, 'comparison_firstcontainer_boilerbrand', '<h2>Searching by Boiler Brands</h2><p>There are a lot of boiler brands out there, some are better than others. WarmZilla doesn’t sell all of the boilers featured in our comparison tool, only the ones we believe offer quality to our customers.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>We’ve written an article on the <a href=\"https://www.warmzilla.co.uk/blog/what-are-the-best-boilers-to-buy-in-2021\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#ff9c00\">Best boilers</font></a> on the market if you want to hear our views on the matter.</p><p><br></p><p>Every boiler in our boiler comparison tool has a complete breakdown of it’s performance and key stats, along with a Which? review score.</p>', NULL, '2021-07-02 08:44:52'),
